  420     r18->size[0] = loop_ub;
  421     emxEnsureCapacity_int32_T(r18, i12);
  422     for (i12 = 0; i12 < loop_ub; i12++) {
  423       r18->data[i12] = i12;
  424     }
  425   
  426     emxInit_real_T1(&r19, 2);
  427     i12 = r19->size[0] * r19->size[1];
  428     r19->size[0] = indices->size[1];
  429     r19->size[1] = 2;
  430     emxEnsureCapacity_real_T(r19, i12);
  431     loop_ub = indices->size[1];
  432     for (i12 = 0; i12 < 2; i12++) {
  433       for (i13 = 0; i13 < loop_ub; i13++) {
  434         r19->data[i13 + r19->size[0] * i12] = b_this->Points->data[((int)
  435           indices->data[indices->size[0] * i13] + b_this->Points->size[0] * i12) -
  436           1];
  437       }
  438     }
  439   
  440     loop_ub = r17->size[0];
  441     b_loop_ub = r18->size[0];
  442     for (i12 = 0; i12 < b_loop_ub; i12++) {
  443       for (i13 = 0; i13 < loop_ub; i13++) {
  444         newBoardCoords->data[newBoardCoords->size[0] * r17->data[i13] +
  445           newBoardCoords->size[0] * newBoardCoords->size[1] * r18->data[i12]] =
  446           r19->data[i13 + loop_ub * i12];
  447       }
  448     }
  449   
  450     emxFree_real_T(&r19);
  451     emxFree_int32_T(&r18);
  452     emxFree_int32_T(&r17);
  453     i12 = !(2 > newBoardCoords->size[0]);
  454     loop_ub = b_this->BoardCoords->size[2];
  455     for (i13 = 0; i13 < loop_ub; i13++) {
  456       b_loop_ub = b_this->BoardCoords->size[1];
  457       for (i14 = 0; i14 < b_loop_ub; i14++) {
  458         c_loop_ub = b_this->BoardCoords->size[0];
  459         for (i15 = 0; i15 < c_loop_ub; i15++) {
  460           newBoardCoords->data[((i12 + i15) + newBoardCoords->size[0] * i14) +
  461             newBoardCoords->size[0] * newBoardCoords->size[1] * i13] =
  462             b_this->BoardCoords->data[(i15 + b_this->BoardCoords->size[0] * i14) +
  463             b_this->BoardCoords->size[0] * b_this->BoardCoords->size[1] * i13];
  464         }
  465       }
  466     }
  467   }
  468   
  469   static void Checkerboard_findClosestIndices(const
  470     c_vision_internal_calibration_c *b_this, const emxArray_real_T
  471     *predictedPoints, emxArray_real_T *indices)
  472   {
  473     int n;
  474     int csz_idx_0;
  475     int i;
  476     emxArray_real32_T *diffs;
  477     emxArray_real32_T *dists;
  478     emxArray_real32_T *a;
  479     emxArray_real32_T *b_diffs;
  480     emxArray_real32_T *c_diffs;
  481     int ib;
  482     int szc;
  483     int acoef;
  484     int k;
  485     float mtmp;
  486     boolean_T exitg1;
  487     n = indices->size[0] * indices->size[1];
  488     indices->size[0] = 1;
  489     indices->size[1] = predictedPoints->size[0];
  490     emxEnsureCapacity_real_T(indices, n);
  491     csz_idx_0 = predictedPoints->size[0];
  492     for (n = 0; n < csz_idx_0; n++) {
  493       indices->data[n] = 0.0;
  494     }
  495   
  496     i = 0;
  497     emxInit_real32_T(&diffs, 2);
  498     emxInit_real32_T1(&dists, 1);
  499     emxInit_real32_T(&a, 2);
  500     emxInit_real32_T1(&b_diffs, 1);
  501     emxInit_real32_T1(&c_diffs, 1);
  502     while (i <= predictedPoints->size[0] - 1) {
  503       n = a->size[0] * a->size[1];
  504       a->size[0] = b_this->Points->size[0];
  505       a->size[1] = 2;
  506       emxEnsureCapacity_real32_T(a, n);
  507       csz_idx_0 = b_this->Points->size[0] * b_this->Points->size[1];
  508       for (n = 0; n < csz_idx_0; n++) {
  509         a->data[n] = b_this->Points->data[n];
  510       }
  511   
  512       csz_idx_0 = a->size[0];
  513       n = diffs->size[0] * diffs->size[1];
  514       diffs->size[0] = csz_idx_0;
  515       diffs->size[1] = 2;
  516       emxEnsureCapacity_real32_T(diffs, n);
  517       if (diffs->size[0] != 0) {
  518         n = predictedPoints->size[1];
  519         csz_idx_0 = (n != 1);
  520         for (n = 0; n < 2; n++) {
  521           ib = csz_idx_0 * n;
  522           szc = diffs->size[0];
  523           acoef = (a->size[0] != 1);
  524           for (k = 0; k < szc; k++) {
  525             diffs->data[k + diffs->size[0] * n] = a->data[acoef * k + a->size[0] *
  526               n] - (float)predictedPoints->data[i + predictedPoints->size[0] * ib];
  527           }
  528         }
  529       }
  530   
  531       csz_idx_0 = diffs->size[0];
  532       n = b_diffs->size[0];
  533       b_diffs->size[0] = csz_idx_0;
  534       emxEnsureCapacity_real32_T1(b_diffs, n);
  535       for (n = 0; n < csz_idx_0; n++) {
  536         b_diffs->data[n] = diffs->data[n];
  537       }
  538   
  539       csz_idx_0 = diffs->size[0];
  540       n = c_diffs->size[0];
  541       c_diffs->size[0] = csz_idx_0;
  542       emxEnsureCapacity_real32_T1(c_diffs, n);
  543       for (n = 0; n < csz_idx_0; n++) {
  544         c_diffs->data[n] = diffs->data[n + diffs->size[0]];
  545       }
  546   
  547       b_hypot(b_diffs, c_diffs, dists);
  548       csz_idx_0 = indices->size[1];
  549       for (n = 0; n < csz_idx_0; n++) {
  550         if ((int)indices->data[n] > 0) {
  551           dists->data[(int)indices->data[n] - 1] = ((real32_T)rtInf);
  552         }
  553       }
  554   
  555       csz_idx_0 = 1;
  556       n = dists->size[0];
  557       mtmp = dists->data[0];
  558       ib = 1;
  559       if (dists->size[0] > 1) {
  560         if (rtIsNaNF(dists->data[0])) {
  561           szc = 2;
  562           exitg1 = false;
  563           while ((!exitg1) && (szc <= n)) {
  564             csz_idx_0 = szc;
  565             if (!rtIsNaNF(dists->data[szc - 1])) {
  566               mtmp = dists->data[szc - 1];
  567               ib = szc;
  568               exitg1 = true;
  569             } else {
  570               szc++;
  571             }
  572           }
  573         }
  574   
  575         if (csz_idx_0 < dists->size[0]) {
  576           while (csz_idx_0 + 1 <= n) {
  577             if (dists->data[csz_idx_0] < mtmp) {
  578               mtmp = dists->data[csz_idx_0];
  579               ib = csz_idx_0 + 1;
  580             }
  581   
  582             csz_idx_0++;
  583           }
  584         }
  585       }
  586   
  587       indices->data[i] = ib;
  588       i++;
  589     }
  590   
  591     emxFree_real32_T(&c_diffs);
  592     emxFree_real32_T(&b_diffs);
  593     emxFree_real32_T(&a);
  594     emxFree_real32_T(&dists);
  595     emxFree_real32_T(&diffs);
  596   }
  597   
  598   static double Checkerboard_findNeighbor(const c_vision_internal_calibration_c
  599     *b_this, const emxArray_real32_T *pointVectors, const emxArray_real32_T
  600     *euclideanDists, const float v[2])
  601   {
  602     double neighborIdx;
  603     emxArray_real32_T *angleCosines;
  604     unsigned int pointVectors_idx_0;
  605     int n;
  606     int m;
  607     int ar;
  608     float b;
  609     int br;
  610     int ic;
  611     emxArray_real32_T *dists;
  612     int ia;
  613     emxArray_boolean_T *r6;
  614     emxArray_int32_T *r7;
  615     emxArray_int32_T *r8;
  616     boolean_T exitg1;
  617     emxInit_real32_T1(&angleCosines, 1);
  618     pointVectors_idx_0 = (unsigned int)pointVectors->size[0];
  619     n = angleCosines->size[0];
  620     angleCosines->size[0] = (int)pointVectors_idx_0;
  621     emxEnsureCapacity_real32_T1(angleCosines, n);
  622     m = pointVectors->size[0];
  623     ar = angleCosines->size[0];
  624     n = angleCosines->size[0];
  625     angleCosines->size[0] = ar;
  626     emxEnsureCapacity_real32_T1(angleCosines, n);
  627     for (n = 0; n < ar; n++) {
  628       angleCosines->data[n] = 0.0F;
  629     }
  630   
  631     if (pointVectors->size[0] != 0) {
  632       ar = 0;
  633       while ((m > 0) && (ar <= 0)) {
  634         for (ic = 1; ic <= m; ic++) {
  635           angleCosines->data[ic - 1] = 0.0F;
  636         }
  637   
  638         ar = m;
  639       }
  640   
  641       br = 0;
  642       ar = 0;
  643       while ((m > 0) && (ar <= 0)) {
  644         ar = -1;
  645         for (n = br; n + 1 <= br + 2; n++) {
  646           if (v[n] != 0.0F) {
  647             ia = ar;
  648             for (ic = 0; ic + 1 <= m; ic++) {
  649               ia++;
  650               angleCosines->data[ic] += v[n] * pointVectors->data[ia];
  651             }
  652           }
  653   
  654           ar += m;
  655         }
  656   
  657         br += 2;
  658         ar = m;
  659       }
  660     }
  661   
  662     b = rt_hypotf_snf(v[0], v[1]);
  663     n = angleCosines->size[0];
  664     emxEnsureCapacity_real32_T1(angleCosines, n);
  665     ar = angleCosines->size[0];
  666     for (n = 0; n < ar; n++) {
  667       angleCosines->data[n] /= euclideanDists->data[n] * b;
  668     }
  669   
  670     emxInit_real32_T1(&dists, 1);
  671     n = dists->size[0];
  672     dists->size[0] = euclideanDists->size[0];
  673     emxEnsureCapacity_real32_T1(dists, n);
  674     ar = euclideanDists->size[0];
  675     for (n = 0; n < ar; n++) {
  676       dists->data[n] = euclideanDists->data[n] + 1.5F * euclideanDists->data[n] *
  677         (1.0F - angleCosines->data[n]);
  678     }
  679   
  680     emxInit_boolean_T(&r6, 2);
  681     n = r6->size[0] * r6->size[1];
  682     r6->size[0] = b_this->BoardIdx->size[0];
  683     r6->size[1] = b_this->BoardIdx->size[1];
  684     emxEnsureCapacity_boolean_T(r6, n);
  685     ar = b_this->BoardIdx->size[0] * b_this->BoardIdx->size[1];
  686     for (n = 0; n < ar; n++) {
  687       r6->data[n] = (b_this->BoardIdx->data[n] > 0.0);
  688     }
  689   
  690     ic = r6->size[0] * r6->size[1] - 1;
  691     ar = 0;
  692     for (n = 0; n <= ic; n++) {
  693       if (r6->data[n]) {
  694         ar++;
  695       }
  696     }
  697   
  698     emxInit_int32_T(&r7, 1);
  699     n = r7->size[0];
  700     r7->size[0] = ar;
  701     emxEnsureCapacity_int32_T(r7, n);
  702     ar = 0;
  703     for (n = 0; n <= ic; n++) {
  704       if (r6->data[n]) {
  705         r7->data[ar] = n + 1;
  706         ar++;
  707       }
  708     }
  709   
  710     emxFree_boolean_T(&r6);
  711     emxInit_int32_T(&r8, 1);
  712     n = r8->size[0];
  713     r8->size[0] = r7->size[0];
  714     emxEnsureCapacity_int32_T(r8, n);
  715     ar = r7->size[0];
  716     for (n = 0; n < ar; n++) {
  717       r8->data[n] = (int)b_this->BoardIdx->data[r7->data[n] - 1];
  718     }
  719   
  720     emxFree_int32_T(&r7);
  721     ar = r8->size[0];
  722     for (n = 0; n < ar; n++) {
  723       dists->data[r8->data[n] - 1] = ((real32_T)rtInf);
  724     }
  725   
  726     emxFree_int32_T(&r8);
  727     ic = angleCosines->size[0];
  728     for (n = 0; n < ic; n++) {
  729       if (angleCosines->data[n] < 0.0F) {
  730         dists->data[n] = ((real32_T)rtInf);
  731       }
  732     }
  733   
  734     emxFree_real32_T(&angleCosines);
  735     ar = 1;
  736     n = dists->size[0];
  737     b = dists->data[0];
  738     ic = 1;
  739     if (dists->size[0] > 1) {
  740       if (rtIsNaNF(dists->data[0])) {
  741         ia = 2;
  742         exitg1 = false;
  743         while ((!exitg1) && (ia <= n)) {
  744           ar = ia;
  745           if (!rtIsNaNF(dists->data[ia - 1])) {
  746             b = dists->data[ia - 1];
  747             ic = ia;
  748             exitg1 = true;
  749           } else {
  750             ia++;
  751           }
  752         }
  753       }
  754   
  755       if (ar < dists->size[0]) {
  756         while (ar + 1 <= n) {
  757           if (dists->data[ar] < b) {
  758             b = dists->data[ar];
  759             ic = ar + 1;
  760           }
  761   
  762           ar++;
  763         }
  764       }
  765     }
  766   
  767     emxFree_real32_T(&dists);
  768     neighborIdx = ic;
  769     if (rtIsInfF(b)) {
  770       neighborIdx = -1.0;
  771     }
  772   
  773     return neighborIdx;
  774   }
  775   
  776   static void Checkerboard_initialize(c_vision_internal_calibration_c *b_this,
  777     double seedIdx, const emxArray_real32_T *points, const float v1[2], const
  778     float v2[2])
  779   {
  780     int ixstart;
  781     int loop_ub;
  782     emxArray_int32_T *r5;
  783     float center[2];
  784     double b_center[2];
  785     emxArray_real32_T *pointVectors;
  786     emxArray_real32_T *b_pointVectors;
  787     emxArray_real32_T *c_pointVectors;
  788     emxArray_real32_T *euclideanDists;
  789     float b_v1[2];
  790     emxArray_boolean_T *c_this;
  791     float r[2];
  792     float l[2];
  793     float d[2];
  794     float u[2];
  795     float boardSize;
  796     float b_l;
  797     emxArray_boolean_T *x;
  798     boolean_T y;
  799     boolean_T exitg1;
  800     float col1[6];
  801     float col2[6];
  802     float row3[6];
  803     float z1[3];
  804     ixstart = b_this->BoardIdx->size[0] * b_this->BoardIdx->size[1];
  805     b_this->BoardIdx->size[0] = 1;
  806     b_this->BoardIdx->size[1] = 1;
  807     emxEnsureCapacity_real_T(b_this->BoardIdx, ixstart);
  808     b_this->BoardIdx->data[0] = 0.0;
  809     ixstart = b_this->BoardIdx->size[0] * b_this->BoardIdx->size[1];
  810     b_this->BoardIdx->size[0] = 3;
  811     b_this->BoardIdx->size[1] = 3;
  812     emxEnsureCapacity_real_T(b_this->BoardIdx, ixstart);
  813     for (ixstart = 0; ixstart < 9; ixstart++) {
  814       b_this->BoardIdx->data[ixstart] = 0.0;
  815     }
  816   
  817     for (ixstart = 0; ixstart < 4; ixstart++) {
  818       b_this->IsDirectionBad[ixstart] = false;
  819     }
  820   
  821     ixstart = b_this->BoardCoords->size[0] * b_this->BoardCoords->size[1] *
  822       b_this->BoardCoords->size[2];
  823     b_this->BoardCoords->size[0] = 1;
  824     b_this->BoardCoords->size[1] = 1;
  825     b_this->BoardCoords->size[2] = 1;
  826     emxEnsureCapacity_real_T1(b_this->BoardCoords, ixstart);
  827     b_this->BoardCoords->data[0] = 0.0;
  828     ixstart = b_this->BoardCoords->size[0] * b_this->BoardCoords->size[1] *
  829       b_this->BoardCoords->size[2];
  830     b_this->BoardCoords->size[0] = 3;
  831     b_this->BoardCoords->size[1] = 3;
  832     b_this->BoardCoords->size[2] = 2;
  833     emxEnsureCapacity_real_T1(b_this->BoardCoords, ixstart);
  834     for (ixstart = 0; ixstart < 18; ixstart++) {
  835       b_this->BoardCoords->data[ixstart] = 0.0;
  836     }
  837   
  838     ixstart = b_this->Points->size[0] * b_this->Points->size[1];
  839     b_this->Points->size[0] = points->size[0];
  840     b_this->Points->size[1] = 2;
  841     emxEnsureCapacity_real32_T(b_this->Points, ixstart);
  842     loop_ub = points->size[0] * points->size[1];
  843     for (ixstart = 0; ixstart < loop_ub; ixstart++) {
  844       b_this->Points->data[ixstart] = points->data[ixstart];
  845     }
  846   
  847     for (ixstart = 0; ixstart < 2; ixstart++) {
  848       center[ixstart] = b_this->Points->data[((int)seedIdx + b_this->Points->size
  849         [0] * ixstart) - 1];
  850     }
  851   
  852     emxInit_int32_T(&r5, 1);
  853     b_this->BoardIdx->data[1 + b_this->BoardIdx->size[0]] = seedIdx;
  854     loop_ub = b_this->BoardCoords->size[2];
  855     ixstart = r5->size[0];
  856     r5->size[0] = loop_ub;
  857     emxEnsureCapacity_int32_T(r5, ixstart);
  858     for (ixstart = 0; ixstart < loop_ub; ixstart++) {
  859       r5->data[ixstart] = ixstart;
  860     }
  861   
  862     for (ixstart = 0; ixstart < 2; ixstart++) {
  863       b_center[ixstart] = center[ixstart];
  864     }
  865   
  866     loop_ub = r5->size[0];
  867     for (ixstart = 0; ixstart < loop_ub; ixstart++) {
  868       b_this->BoardCoords->data[(b_this->BoardCoords->size[0] +
  869         b_this->BoardCoords->size[0] * b_this->BoardCoords->size[1] * r5->
  870         data[ixstart]) + 1] = b_center[ixstart];
  871     }
  872   
  873     emxInit_real32_T(&pointVectors, 2);
  874     emxInit_real32_T1(&b_pointVectors, 1);
  875     b_this->LastExpandDirection = 1.0;
  876     b_this->PreviousEnergy = ((real32_T)rtInf);
  877     b_this->isValid = false;
  878     bsxfun(b_this->Points, center, pointVectors);
  879     loop_ub = pointVectors->size[0];
  880     ixstart = b_pointVectors->size[0];
  881     b_pointVectors->size[0] = loop_ub;
  882     emxEnsureCapacity_real32_T1(b_pointVectors, ixstart);
  883     for (ixstart = 0; ixstart < loop_ub; ixstart++) {
  884       b_pointVectors->data[ixstart] = pointVectors->data[ixstart];
  885     }
  886   
  887     emxInit_real32_T1(&c_pointVectors, 1);
  888     loop_ub = pointVectors->size[0];
  889     ixstart = c_pointVectors->size[0];
  890     c_pointVectors->size[0] = loop_ub;
  891     emxEnsureCapacity_real32_T1(c_pointVectors, ixstart);
  892     for (ixstart = 0; ixstart < loop_ub; ixstart++) {
  893       c_pointVectors->data[ixstart] = pointVectors->data[ixstart +
  894         pointVectors->size[0]];
  895     }
  896   
  897     emxInit_real32_T1(&euclideanDists, 1);
  898     b_hypot(b_pointVectors, c_pointVectors, euclideanDists);
  899     b_this->BoardIdx->data[1 + (b_this->BoardIdx->size[0] << 1)] =
  900       Checkerboard_findNeighbor(b_this, pointVectors, euclideanDists, v1);
  901     emxFree_real32_T(&c_pointVectors);
  902     emxFree_real32_T(&b_pointVectors);
  903     for (ixstart = 0; ixstart < 2; ixstart++) {
  904       b_v1[ixstart] = -v1[ixstart];
  905     }
  906   
  907     b_this->BoardIdx->data[1] = Checkerboard_findNeighbor(b_this, pointVectors,
  908       euclideanDists, b_v1);
  909     b_this->BoardIdx->data[2 + b_this->BoardIdx->size[0]] =
  910       Checkerboard_findNeighbor(b_this, pointVectors, euclideanDists, v2);
  911     for (ixstart = 0; ixstart < 2; ixstart++) {
  912       b_v1[ixstart] = -v2[ixstart];
  913     }
  914   
  915     emxInit_boolean_T1(&c_this, 1);
  916     b_this->BoardIdx->data[b_this->BoardIdx->size[0]] = Checkerboard_findNeighbor
  917       (b_this, pointVectors, euclideanDists, b_v1);
  918     ixstart = c_this->size[0];
  919     c_this->size[0] = b_this->BoardIdx->size[0] * b_this->BoardIdx->size[1];
  920     emxEnsureCapacity_boolean_T1(c_this, ixstart);
  921     loop_ub = b_this->BoardIdx->size[0] * b_this->BoardIdx->size[1];
  922     for (ixstart = 0; ixstart < loop_ub; ixstart++) {
  923       c_this->data[ixstart] = (b_this->BoardIdx->data[ixstart] < 0.0);
  924     }
  925   
  926     if (any(c_this)) {
  927       b_this->isValid = false;
  928     } else {
  929       loop_ub = (int)b_this->BoardIdx->data[1 + (b_this->BoardIdx->size[0] << 1)];
  930       for (ixstart = 0; ixstart < 2; ixstart++) {

 1621   static void b_imfilter(emxArray_real32_T *varargin_1)

 1639     int lastColB;

 1650     pad[0] = 0.0;

 1668         iv3[cidx] = b_a->size[cidx];
 1669       }

 1672       cidx = result->size[0] * result->size[1];
 1673       result->size[0] = iv3[0];

 1694           firstColB = 2;

 1696           firstColB = 0;
 1697         }
 1698

 1700           lastColB = 2;
 1701         } else {

 1706           lastRowB = 1;
 1707         } else {
 1708           lastRowB = iv3[0];
 1709         }
 1710

 1712           if (firstColB + na < cEnd) {
 1713             lastColA = na;
 1714           } else {
 1715             lastColA = cEnd - firstColB;
 1716           }
 1717

 1751         }

 1757       } else {

 1759       }

 1762         cidx = 0;

 1764       } else {

 1767       }
 1768

 1785   static void b_merge(int idx[4], double x[4], int offset, int np, int nq, int
 1786                       iwork[4], double xwork[4])
 1787   {
 1788     int n;
 1789     int qend;
 1790     int p;
 1791     int iout;
 1792     int exitg1;
 1793     if (nq != 0) {
 1794       n = np + nq;
 1795       for (qend = 0; qend + 1 <= n; qend++) {
 1796         iwork[qend] = idx[offset + qend];
 1797         xwork[qend] = x[offset + qend];
 1798       }
 1799   
 1800       p = 0;
 1801       n = np;
 1802       qend = np + nq;
 1803       iout = offset - 1;
 1804       do {
 1805         exitg1 = 0;
 1806         iout++;
 1807         if (xwork[p] <= xwork[n]) {
 1808           idx[iout] = iwork[p];
 1809           x[iout] = xwork[p];
 1810           if (p + 1 < np) {
 1811             p++;
 1812           } else {
 1813             exitg1 = 1;
 1814           }
 1815         } else {
 1816           idx[iout] = iwork[n];
 1817           x[iout] = xwork[n];
 1818           if (n + 1 < qend) {
 1819             n++;
 1820           } else {
 1821             n = (iout - p) + 1;
 1822             while (p + 1 <= np) {
 1823               idx[n + p] = iwork[p];
 1824               x[n + p] = xwork[p];
 1825               p++;
 1826             }
 1827   
 1828             exitg1 = 1;
 1829           }
 1830         }
 1831       } while (exitg1 == 0);
 1832     }
 1833   }

 1835   static double b_mod(double x)
 1836   {
 1837     double r;
 1838     if ((!rtIsInf(x)) && (!rtIsNaN(x))) {
 1839       if (x == 0.0) {
 1840         r = 0.0;
 1841       } else {
 1842         r = std::fmod(x, 2.0);
 1843         if (r == 0.0) {
 1844           r = 0.0;
 1845         }
 1846       }
 1847     } else {
 1848       r = rtNaN;
 1849     }
 1850   
 1851     return r;
 1852   }

 1854   static void b_rot90(const emxArray_real_T *A, emxArray_real_T *B)
 1855   {
 1856     int m;
 1857     int n;
 1858     int j;
 1859     int i;
 1860     int A_idx_0;
 1861     int B_idx_0;
 1862     m = A->size[0];
 1863     n = A->size[1];
 1864     j = B->size[0] * B->size[1];
 1865     B->size[0] = A->size[0];
 1866     B->size[1] = A->size[1];
 1867     emxEnsureCapacity_real_T(B, j);
 1868     for (j = 1; j <= n; j++) {
 1869       for (i = 1; i <= m; i++) {
 1870         A_idx_0 = A->size[0];
 1871         B_idx_0 = B->size[0];
 1872         B->data[(i + B_idx_0 * (j - 1)) - 1] = A->data[(m - i) + A_idx_0 * (n - j)];
 1873       }
 1874     }
 1875   }

 1877   static void b_sort(emxArray_real32_T *x, int dim, emxArray_int32_T *idx)
 1878   {
 1879     int i45;
 1880     emxArray_real32_T *vwork;
 1881     int vstride;
 1882     int x_idx_0;
 1883     int j;
 1884     emxArray_int32_T *iidx;
 1885     if (dim <= 1) {
 1886       i45 = x->size[0];
 1887     } else {
 1888       i45 = 1;
 1889     }
 1890   
 1891     emxInit_real32_T1(&vwork, 1);
 1892     vstride = vwork->size[0];
 1893     vwork->size[0] = i45;
 1894     emxEnsureCapacity_real32_T1(vwork, vstride);
 1895     x_idx_0 = x->size[0];
 1896     vstride = idx->size[0];
 1897     idx->size[0] = x_idx_0;
 1898     emxEnsureCapacity_int32_T(idx, vstride);
 1899     vstride = 1;
 1900     x_idx_0 = 1;
 1901     while (x_idx_0 <= dim - 1) {
 1902       vstride *= x->size[0];
 1903       x_idx_0 = 2;
 1904     }
 1905   
 1906     j = 0;
 1907     emxInit_int32_T(&iidx, 1);
 1908     while (j + 1 <= vstride) {
 1909       for (x_idx_0 = 0; x_idx_0 + 1 <= i45; x_idx_0++) {
 1910         vwork->data[x_idx_0] = x->data[j + x_idx_0 * vstride];
 1911       }
 1912   
 1913       sortIdx(vwork, iidx);
 1914       for (x_idx_0 = 0; x_idx_0 + 1 <= i45; x_idx_0++) {
 1915         x->data[j + x_idx_0 * vstride] = vwork->data[x_idx_0];
 1916         idx->data[j + x_idx_0 * vstride] = iidx->data[x_idx_0];
 1917       }
 1918   
 1919       j++;
 1920     }
 1921   
 1922     emxFree_int32_T(&iidx);
 1923     emxFree_real32_T(&vwork);
 1924   }

 1926   static void b_squeeze(const emxArray_real_T *a, emxArray_real_T *b)
 1927   {
 1928     int k;
 1929     int i21;
 1930     int sqsz[3];
 1931     k = 3;
 1932     while ((k > 2) && (a->size[2] == 1)) {
 1933       k = 2;
 1934     }
 1935   
 1936     if (k <= 2) {
 1937       sqsz[0] = a->size[0];
 1938       i21 = b->size[0] * b->size[1];
 1939       b->size[0] = sqsz[0];
 1940       b->size[1] = 1;
 1941       emxEnsureCapacity_real_T(b, i21);
 1942       i21 = a->size[0] * a->size[2];
 1943       for (k = 0; k + 1 <= i21; k++) {
 1944         b->data[k] = a->data[k];
 1945       }
 1946     } else {
 1947       for (i21 = 0; i21 < 3; i21++) {
 1948         sqsz[i21] = 1;
 1949       }
 1950   
 1951       k = 0;
 1952       if (a->size[0] != 1) {
 1953         sqsz[0] = a->size[0];
 1954         k = 1;
 1955       }
 1956   
 1957       if (a->size[2] != 1) {
 1958         sqsz[k] = a->size[2];
 1959       }
 1960   
 1961       i21 = b->size[0] * b->size[1];
 1962       b->size[0] = sqsz[0];
 1963       b->size[1] = sqsz[1];
 1964       emxEnsureCapacity_real_T(b, i21);
 1965       i21 = a->size[0] * a->size[2];
 1966       for (k = 0; k + 1 <= i21; k++) {
 1967         b->data[k] = a->data[k];
 1968       }
 1969     }
 1970   }

 1973                      emxArray_real32_T *c)
 1974   {
 1975     int csz_idx_0;
 1976     int k;
 1977     int szc;
 1978     int b_k;

 1980     k = c->size[0] * c->size[1];
 1981     c->size[0] = csz_idx_0;
 1982     c->size[1] = 2;
 1983     emxEnsureCapacity_real32_T(c, k);
 1984     if (c->size[0] != 0) {
 1985       csz_idx_0 = (a->size[0] != 1);
 1986       for (k = 0; k < 2; k++) {
 1987         szc = c->size[0];
 1988         for (b_k = 0; b_k < szc; b_k++) {
 1989           c->data[b_k + c->size[0] * k] = a->data[csz_idx_0 * b_k + a->size[0] * k]
 1990             - b[k];
 1991         }
 1992       }
 1993     }
 1994   }

 2050     int lookUpInd;

 2131           ((int)inDims[1] - 2)] << 1) + (bw->data[1 + bw->size[0] * ((int)inDims[1]

 2160

 2162             + (bwin->data[(int)inDims[0] - 1] << 4)];

 2164   
 2165         if ((int)inDims[1] > 1) {

 2174             [0] * ((int)inDims[1] - 2)] << 1) + (bwin->data[bwin->size[0] * ((int)
 2175             inDims[1] - 1)] << 4)];

 2178     }
 2179   
 2180     emxFree_boolean_T(&bw);
 2181   }

 2464           b_this->BoardCoords->size[0] * b_this->BoardCoords->size[1] * i16];

 2466

 2501       } else {

 2503       }
 2504

 2506     }
 2507

 2512     return newEnergy * (float)ixstart - (float)(b_this->BoardIdx->size[0] *
 2513       b_this->BoardIdx->size[1]);
 2514   }

 3785   static void cornerOrientations(const emxArray_real32_T *Ix2, const
 3786     emxArray_real32_T *Iy2, const emxArray_real32_T *Ixy, const float p[2], float
 3787     v1[2], float v2[2])
 3788   {
 3789     float df;
 3790     float adf;
 3791     float tb;
 3792     float ab;
 3793     float rt;
 3794     int sgn1;
 3795     int sgn2;
 3796     float sn1[2];
 3797     float cs1[2];
 3798     static const float fv0[4] = { 0.707106769F, 0.707106769F, -0.707106769F,
 3799       0.707106769F };
 3800   
 3801     df = Ix2->data[((int)p[1] + Ix2->size[0] * ((int)p[0] - 1)) - 1] - Iy2->data
 3802       [((int)p[1] + Iy2->size[0] * ((int)p[0] - 1)) - 1];
 3803     adf = std::abs(df);
 3804     tb = Ixy->data[((int)p[1] + Ixy->size[0] * ((int)p[0] - 1)) - 1] + Ixy->data
 3805       [((int)p[1] + Ixy->size[0] * ((int)p[0] - 1)) - 1];
 3806     ab = std::abs(tb);
 3807     if (adf > ab) {
 3808       rt = ab / adf;
 3809       rt = adf * std::sqrt(1.0F + rt * rt);
 3810     } else if (adf < ab) {
 3811       rt = adf / ab;
 3812       rt = ab * std::sqrt(1.0F + rt * rt);
 3813     } else {
 3814       rt = ab * 1.41421354F;
 3815     }
 3816   
 3817     if (Ix2->data[((int)p[1] + Ix2->size[0] * ((int)p[0] - 1)) - 1] + Iy2->data
 3818         [((int)p[1] + Iy2->size[0] * ((int)p[0] - 1)) - 1] < 0.0F) {
 3819       sgn1 = -1;
 3820     } else {
 3821       sgn1 = 1;
 3822     }
 3823   
 3824     if (df > 0.0F) {
 3825       rt += df;
 3826       sgn2 = 1;
 3827     } else {
 3828       rt = df - rt;
 3829       sgn2 = -1;
 3830     }
 3831   
 3832     if (std::abs(rt) > ab) {
 3833       rt = -tb / rt;
 3834       df = 1.0F / std::sqrt(1.0F + rt * rt);
 3835       adf = rt * df;
 3836     } else if (ab == 0.0F) {
 3837       adf = 1.0F;
 3838       df = 0.0F;
 3839     } else {
 3840       rt = -rt / tb;
 3841       adf = 1.0F / std::sqrt(1.0F + rt * rt);
 3842       df = rt * adf;
 3843     }
 3844   
 3845     if (sgn1 == sgn2) {
 3846       rt = adf;
 3847       adf = -df;
 3848       df = rt;
 3849     }
 3850   
 3851     sn1[0] = -df;
 3852     sn1[1] = adf;
 3853     cs1[0] = adf;
 3854     cs1[1] = df;
 3855     for (sgn1 = 0; sgn1 < 2; sgn1++) {
 3856       v1[sgn1] = 0.0F;
 3857       v2[sgn1] = 0.0F;
 3858       for (sgn2 = 0; sgn2 < 2; sgn2++) {
 3859         v1[sgn1] += sn1[sgn2] * fv0[sgn2 + (sgn1 << 1)];
 3860         v2[sgn1] += cs1[sgn2] * fv0[sgn2 + (sgn1 << 1)];
 3861       }
 3862     }
 3863   }

 5043   
 5044   static int div_s32(int numerator, int denominator)
 5045   {
 5046     int quotient;
 5047     unsigned int absNumerator;
 5048     unsigned int absDenominator;
 5049     boolean_T quotientNeedsNegation;
 5050     if (denominator == 0) {
 5051       if (numerator >= 0) {
 5052         quotient = MAX_int32_T;
 5053       } else {
 5054         quotient = MIN_int32_T;
 5055       }
 5056     } else {
 5057       if (numerator < 0) {
 5058         absNumerator = ~(unsigned int)numerator + 1U;
 5059       } else {
 5060         absNumerator = (unsigned int)numerator;
 5061       }
 5062   
 5063       if (denominator < 0) {
 5064         absDenominator = ~(unsigned int)denominator + 1U;
 5065       } else {
 5066         absDenominator = (unsigned int)denominator;
 5067       }
 5068   
 5069       quotientNeedsNegation = ((numerator < 0) != (denominator < 0));
 5070       absNumerator /= absDenominator;
 5071       if (quotientNeedsNegation) {
 5072         quotient = -(int)absNumerator;
 5073       } else {
 5074         quotient = (int)absNumerator;
 5075       }
 5076     }
 5077   
 5078     return quotient;
 5079   }
 5080   
 5081   static int div_s32_floor(int numerator, int denominator)
 5082   {
 5083     int quotient;
 5084     unsigned int absNumerator;
 5085     unsigned int absDenominator;
 5086     boolean_T quotientNeedsNegation;
 5087     unsigned int tempAbsQuotient;
 5088     if (denominator == 0) {
 5089       if (numerator >= 0) {
 5090         quotient = MAX_int32_T;
 5091       } else {
 5092         quotient = MIN_int32_T;
 5093       }
 5094     } else {
 5095       if (numerator < 0) {
 5096         absNumerator = ~(unsigned int)numerator + 1U;
 5097       } else {
 5098         absNumerator = (unsigned int)numerator;
 5099       }
 5100   
 5101       if (denominator < 0) {
 5102         absDenominator = ~(unsigned int)denominator + 1U;
 5103       } else {
 5104         absDenominator = (unsigned int)denominator;
 5105       }
 5106   
 5107       quotientNeedsNegation = ((numerator < 0) != (denominator < 0));
 5108       tempAbsQuotient = absNumerator / absDenominator;
 5109       if (quotientNeedsNegation) {
 5110         absNumerator %= absDenominator;
 5111         if (absNumerator > 0U) {
 5112           tempAbsQuotient++;
 5113         }
 5114   
 5115         quotient = -(int)tempAbsQuotient;
 5116       } else {
 5117         quotient = (int)tempAbsQuotient;
 5118       }
 5119     }
 5120   
 5121     return quotient;
 5122   }

 5450     emxFree_real_T(&d_num);
 5451     ixstart = b_this->BoardIdx->size[0] * b_this->BoardIdx->size[1];
 5452     return newEnergy * (float)ixstart - (float)(b_this->BoardIdx->size[0] *

 5454   }
 5455   
 5456   static void find_peaks(const emxArray_real32_T *metric, emxArray_real32_T *loc)
 5457   {
 5458     int ixstart;
 5459     int n;
 5460     float threshold;
 5461     int idx;
 5462     emxArray_boolean_T *bw;
 5463     int i2;
 5464     boolean_T exitg1;
 5465     emxArray_int32_T *ii;
 5466     emxArray_int32_T *b_idx;
 5467     unsigned int siz[2];
 5468     emxArray_int32_T *vk;
 5469     ixstart = 1;
 5470     n = metric->size[0] * metric->size[1];
 5471     threshold = metric->data[0];
 5472     if (metric->size[0] * metric->size[1] > 1) {
 5473       if (rtIsNaNF(metric->data[0])) {
 5474         idx = 2;
 5475         exitg1 = false;
 5476         while ((!exitg1) && (idx <= n)) {
 5477           ixstart = idx;
 5478           if (!rtIsNaNF(metric->data[idx - 1])) {
 5479             threshold = metric->data[idx - 1];
 5480             exitg1 = true;
 5481           } else {
 5482             idx++;
 5483           }
 5484         }
 5485       }
 5486   
 5487       if (ixstart < metric->size[0] * metric->size[1]) {
 5488         while (ixstart + 1 <= n) {
 5489           if (metric->data[ixstart] > threshold) {
 5490             threshold = metric->data[ixstart];
 5491           }
 5492   
 5493           ixstart++;
 5494         }
 5495       }
 5496     }
 5497   
 5498     if (threshold <= 4.94065645841247E-324) {
 5499       i2 = loc->size[0] * loc->size[1];
 5500       loc->size[0] = 0;
 5501       loc->size[1] = 2;
 5502       emxEnsureCapacity_real32_T(loc, i2);
 5503     } else {
 5504       emxInit_boolean_T(&bw, 2);
 5505       imregionalmax(metric, bw);
 5506       threshold *= 0.15F;
 5507       idx = metric->size[0] * metric->size[1] - 1;
 5508       ixstart = 0;
 5509       for (n = 0; n <= idx; n++) {
 5510         if (metric->data[n] < threshold) {
 5511           ixstart++;
 5512         }
 5513       }
 5514   
 5515       emxInit_int32_T(&ii, 1);
 5516       i2 = ii->size[0];
 5517       ii->size[0] = ixstart;
 5518       emxEnsureCapacity_int32_T(ii, i2);
 5519       ixstart = 0;
 5520       for (n = 0; n <= idx; n++) {
 5521         if (metric->data[n] < threshold) {
 5522           ii->data[ixstart] = n + 1;
 5523           ixstart++;
 5524         }
 5525       }
 5526   
 5527       ixstart = ii->size[0];
 5528       for (i2 = 0; i2 < ixstart; i2++) {
 5529         bw->data[ii->data[i2] - 1] = false;
 5530       }
 5531   
 5532       if (!((bw->size[0] == 0) || (bw->size[1] == 0))) {
 5533         algbwmorph(bw);
 5534       }
 5535   
 5536       ixstart = bw->size[1];
 5537       for (i2 = 0; i2 < ixstart; i2++) {
 5538         bw->data[bw->size[0] * i2] = false;
 5539       }
 5540   
 5541       ixstart = bw->size[1];
 5542       n = bw->size[0] - 1;
 5543       for (i2 = 0; i2 < ixstart; i2++) {
 5544         bw->data[n + bw->size[0] * i2] = false;
 5545       }
 5546   
 5547       ixstart = bw->size[0];
 5548       for (i2 = 0; i2 < ixstart; i2++) {
 5549         bw->data[i2] = false;
 5550       }
 5551   
 5552       ixstart = bw->size[0];
 5553       n = bw->size[1] - 1;
 5554       for (i2 = 0; i2 < ixstart; i2++) {
 5555         bw->data[i2 + bw->size[0] * n] = false;
 5556       }
 5557   
 5558       n = bw->size[0] * bw->size[1];
 5559       idx = 0;
 5560       i2 = ii->size[0];
 5561       ii->size[0] = n;
 5562       emxEnsureCapacity_int32_T(ii, i2);
 5563       ixstart = 1;
 5564       exitg1 = false;
 5565       while ((!exitg1) && (ixstart <= n)) {
 5566         if (bw->data[ixstart - 1]) {
 5567           idx++;
 5568           ii->data[idx - 1] = ixstart;
 5569           if (idx >= n) {
 5570             exitg1 = true;
 5571           } else {
 5572             ixstart++;
 5573           }
 5574         } else {
 5575           ixstart++;
 5576         }
 5577       }
 5578   
 5579       emxFree_boolean_T(&bw);
 5580       if (n == 1) {
 5581         if (idx == 0) {
 5582           i2 = ii->size[0];
 5583           ii->size[0] = 0;
 5584           emxEnsureCapacity_int32_T(ii, i2);
 5585         }
 5586       } else {
 5587         i2 = ii->size[0];
 5588         if (1 > idx) {
 5589           ii->size[0] = 0;
 5590         } else {
 5591           ii->size[0] = idx;
 5592         }
 5593   
 5594         emxEnsureCapacity_int32_T(ii, i2);
 5595       }
 5596   
 5597       emxInit_int32_T(&b_idx, 1);
 5598       i2 = b_idx->size[0];
 5599       b_idx->size[0] = ii->size[0];
 5600       emxEnsureCapacity_int32_T(b_idx, i2);
 5601       ixstart = ii->size[0];
 5602       for (i2 = 0; i2 < ixstart; i2++) {
 5603         b_idx->data[i2] = ii->data[i2];
 5604       }
 5605   
 5606       ixstart = b_idx->size[0];
 5607       i2 = loc->size[0] * loc->size[1];
 5608       loc->size[0] = ixstart;
 5609       loc->size[1] = 2;
 5610       emxEnsureCapacity_real32_T(loc, i2);
 5611       ixstart <<= 1;
 5612       for (i2 = 0; i2 < ixstart; i2++) {
 5613         loc->data[i2] = 0.0F;
 5614       }
 5615   
 5616       for (i2 = 0; i2 < 2; i2++) {
 5617         siz[i2] = (unsigned int)metric->size[i2];
 5618       }
 5619   
 5620       i2 = ii->size[0];
 5621       ii->size[0] = b_idx->size[0];
 5622       emxEnsureCapacity_int32_T(ii, i2);
 5623       ixstart = b_idx->size[0];
 5624       for (i2 = 0; i2 < ixstart; i2++) {
 5625         ii->data[i2] = b_idx->data[i2] - 1;
 5626       }
 5627   
 5628       emxFree_int32_T(&b_idx);
 5629       emxInit_int32_T(&vk, 1);
 5630       i2 = vk->size[0];
 5631       vk->size[0] = ii->size[0];
 5632       emxEnsureCapacity_int32_T(vk, i2);
 5633       ixstart = ii->size[0];
 5634       for (i2 = 0; i2 < ixstart; i2++) {
 5635         vk->data[i2] = div_s32(ii->data[i2], (int)siz[0]);
 5636       }
 5637   
 5638       i2 = ii->size[0];
 5639       emxEnsureCapacity_int32_T(ii, i2);
 5640       ixstart = ii->size[0];
 5641       for (i2 = 0; i2 < ixstart; i2++) {
 5642         ii->data[i2] -= vk->data[i2] * (int)siz[0];
 5643       }
 5644   
 5645       ixstart = ii->size[0];
 5646       for (i2 = 0; i2 < ixstart; i2++) {
 5647         loc->data[i2 + loc->size[0]] = (float)(ii->data[i2] + 1);
 5648       }
 5649   
 5650       emxFree_int32_T(&ii);
 5651       ixstart = vk->size[0];
 5652       for (i2 = 0; i2 < ixstart; i2++) {
 5653         loc->data[i2] = (float)(vk->data[i2] + 1);
 5654       }
 5655   
 5656       emxFree_int32_T(&vk);
 5657     }
 5658   }
 5659   
 5660   static c_vision_internal_calibration_c *growCheckerboard(const emxArray_real32_T
 5661     *points, const emxArray_real32_T *scores, const emxArray_real32_T *Ix2, const
 5662     emxArray_real32_T *Iy2, const emxArray_real32_T *Ixy, double theta,
 5663     c_vision_internal_calibration_c *iobj_0, c_vision_internal_calibration_c
 5664     *iobj_1, c_vision_internal_calibration_c *iobj_2)
 5665   {
 5666     c_vision_internal_calibration_c *board;
 5667     emxArray_real_T *seedIdx;
 5668     int i4;
 5669     int i5;
 5670     int loop_ub;
 5671     emxArray_real32_T *x;
 5672     emxArray_int32_T *sortedIdx;
 5673     emxArray_int32_T *iidx;
 5674     emxArray_uint32_T *b_seedIdx;
 5675     int b_x;
 5676     c_vision_internal_calibration_c *currentBoard;
 5677     int i;
 5678     emxArray_real_T *b_currentBoard;
 5679     emxArray_real_T *c_currentBoard;
 5680     float c_x[2];
 5681     float v1[2];
 5682     float v2[2];
 5683     boolean_T hasExpanded;
 5684     c_vision_internal_calibration_c *tmpBoard;
 5685     int b_i;
 5686     int exitg1;
 5687     double d0;
 5688     int i6;
 5689     int b_loop_ub;
 5690     int d_currentBoard;
 5691     int i7;
 5692     if (scores->size[0] == 0) {
 5693       iobj_2->isValid = false;
 5694       iobj_2->Energy = ((real32_T)rtInf);
 5695       board = iobj_2;
 5696       i4 = iobj_2->BoardIdx->size[0] * iobj_2->BoardIdx->size[1];
 5697       iobj_2->BoardIdx->size[0] = 1;
 5698       iobj_2->BoardIdx->size[1] = 1;
 5699       emxEnsureCapacity_real_T(iobj_2->BoardIdx, i4);
 5700       iobj_2->BoardIdx->data[0] = 0.0;
 5701       i4 = iobj_2->BoardIdx->size[0] * iobj_2->BoardIdx->size[1];
 5702       iobj_2->BoardIdx->size[0] = 3;
 5703       iobj_2->BoardIdx->size[1] = 3;
 5704       emxEnsureCapacity_real_T(iobj_2->BoardIdx, i4);
 5705       for (i4 = 0; i4 < 9; i4++) {
 5706         iobj_2->BoardIdx->data[i4] = 0.0;
 5707       }
 5708   
 5709       i4 = iobj_2->BoardCoords->size[0] * iobj_2->BoardCoords->size[1] *
 5710         iobj_2->BoardCoords->size[2];
 5711       iobj_2->BoardCoords->size[0] = 1;
 5712       iobj_2->BoardCoords->size[1] = 1;
 5713       iobj_2->BoardCoords->size[2] = 1;
 5714       emxEnsureCapacity_real_T1(iobj_2->BoardCoords, i4);
 5715       iobj_2->BoardCoords->data[0] = 0.0;
 5716       i4 = iobj_2->BoardCoords->size[0] * iobj_2->BoardCoords->size[1] *
 5717         iobj_2->BoardCoords->size[2];
 5718       iobj_2->BoardCoords->size[0] = 3;
 5719       iobj_2->BoardCoords->size[1] = 3;
 5720       iobj_2->BoardCoords->size[2] = 2;
 5721       emxEnsureCapacity_real_T1(iobj_2->BoardCoords, i4);
 5722       for (i4 = 0; i4 < 18; i4++) {
 5723         iobj_2->BoardCoords->data[i4] = 0.0;
 5724       }
 5725     } else {
 5726       emxInit_real_T1(&seedIdx, 2);
 5727       if (points->size[0] < 1) {
 5728         i4 = seedIdx->size[0] * seedIdx->size[1];
 5729         seedIdx->size[0] = 1;
 5730         seedIdx->size[1] = 0;
 5731         emxEnsureCapacity_real_T(seedIdx, i4);
 5732       } else {
 5733         i4 = points->size[0];
 5734         i5 = seedIdx->size[0] * seedIdx->size[1];
 5735         seedIdx->size[0] = 1;
 5736         seedIdx->size[1] = (int)((double)i4 - 1.0) + 1;
 5737         emxEnsureCapacity_real_T(seedIdx, i5);
 5738         loop_ub = (int)((double)i4 - 1.0);
 5739         for (i4 = 0; i4 <= loop_ub; i4++) {
 5740           seedIdx->data[seedIdx->size[0] * i4] = 1.0 + (double)i4;
 5741         }
 5742       }
 5743   
 5744       emxInit_real32_T1(&x, 1);
 5745       i4 = x->size[0];
 5746       x->size[0] = seedIdx->size[1];
 5747       emxEnsureCapacity_real32_T1(x, i4);
 5748       loop_ub = seedIdx->size[1];
 5749       for (i4 = 0; i4 < loop_ub; i4++) {
 5750         x->data[i4] = scores->data[(int)seedIdx->data[seedIdx->size[0] * i4] - 1];
 5751       }
 5752   
 5753       emxInit_int32_T(&sortedIdx, 1);
 5754       emxInit_int32_T(&iidx, 1);
 5755       sort(x, iidx);
 5756       i4 = sortedIdx->size[0];
 5757       sortedIdx->size[0] = iidx->size[0];
 5758       emxEnsureCapacity_int32_T(sortedIdx, i4);
 5759       loop_ub = iidx->size[0];
 5760       emxFree_real32_T(&x);
 5761       for (i4 = 0; i4 < loop_ub; i4++) {
 5762         sortedIdx->data[i4] = iidx->data[i4];
 5763       }
 5764   
 5765       emxFree_int32_T(&iidx);
 5766       emxInit_uint32_T(&b_seedIdx, 2);
 5767       i4 = b_seedIdx->size[0] * b_seedIdx->size[1];
 5768       b_seedIdx->size[0] = 1;
 5769       b_seedIdx->size[1] = seedIdx->size[1];
 5770       emxEnsureCapacity_uint32_T(b_seedIdx, i4);
 5771       loop_ub = seedIdx->size[1];
 5772       for (i4 = 0; i4 < loop_ub; i4++) {
 5773         b_seedIdx->data[b_seedIdx->size[0] * i4] = (unsigned int)seedIdx->
 5774           data[seedIdx->size[0] * i4];
 5775       }
 5776   
 5777       i4 = seedIdx->size[0] * seedIdx->size[1];
 5778       seedIdx->size[0] = 1;
 5779       seedIdx->size[1] = sortedIdx->size[0];
 5780       emxEnsureCapacity_real_T(seedIdx, i4);
 5781       loop_ub = sortedIdx->size[0];
 5782       for (i4 = 0; i4 < loop_ub; i4++) {
 5783         seedIdx->data[seedIdx->size[0] * i4] = b_seedIdx->data[sortedIdx->data[i4]
 5784           - 1];
 5785       }
 5786   
 5787       if (sortedIdx->size[0] > 2000) {
 5788         b_x = (int)rt_roundd_snf((double)seedIdx->size[1] / 2.0);
 5789         if (2000 < b_x) {
 5790           b_x = 2000;
 5791         }
 5792   
 5793         if (1 > b_x) {
 5794           loop_ub = 0;
 5795         } else {
 5796           loop_ub = b_x;
 5797         }
 5798   
 5799         i4 = b_seedIdx->size[0] * b_seedIdx->size[1];
 5800         b_seedIdx->size[0] = 1;
 5801         b_seedIdx->size[1] = seedIdx->size[1];
 5802         emxEnsureCapacity_uint32_T(b_seedIdx, i4);
 5803         b_x = seedIdx->size[1];
 5804         for (i4 = 0; i4 < b_x; i4++) {
 5805           b_seedIdx->data[b_seedIdx->size[0] * i4] = (unsigned int)seedIdx->
 5806             data[seedIdx->size[0] * i4];
 5807         }
 5808   
 5809         i4 = seedIdx->size[0] * seedIdx->size[1];
 5810         seedIdx->size[0] = 1;
 5811         seedIdx->size[1] = loop_ub;
 5812         emxEnsureCapacity_real_T(seedIdx, i4);
 5813         for (i4 = 0; i4 < loop_ub; i4++) {
 5814           seedIdx->data[seedIdx->size[0] * i4] = b_seedIdx->data[i4];
 5815         }
 5816       }
 5817   
 5818       emxFree_int32_T(&sortedIdx);
 5819       iobj_0->isValid = false;
 5820       iobj_0->Energy = ((real32_T)rtInf);
 5821       board = iobj_0;
 5822       i4 = iobj_0->BoardIdx->size[0] * iobj_0->BoardIdx->size[1];
 5823       iobj_0->BoardIdx->size[0] = 1;
 5824       iobj_0->BoardIdx->size[1] = 1;
 5825       emxEnsureCapacity_real_T(iobj_0->BoardIdx, i4);
 5826       iobj_0->BoardIdx->data[0] = 0.0;
 5827       i4 = iobj_0->BoardIdx->size[0] * iobj_0->BoardIdx->size[1];
 5828       iobj_0->BoardIdx->size[0] = 3;
 5829       iobj_0->BoardIdx->size[1] = 3;
 5830       emxEnsureCapacity_real_T(iobj_0->BoardIdx, i4);
 5831       for (i4 = 0; i4 < 9; i4++) {
 5832         iobj_0->BoardIdx->data[i4] = 0.0;
 5833       }
 5834   
 5835       i4 = iobj_0->BoardCoords->size[0] * iobj_0->BoardCoords->size[1] *
 5836         iobj_0->BoardCoords->size[2];
 5837       iobj_0->BoardCoords->size[0] = 1;
 5838       iobj_0->BoardCoords->size[1] = 1;
 5839       iobj_0->BoardCoords->size[2] = 1;
 5840       emxEnsureCapacity_real_T1(iobj_0->BoardCoords, i4);
 5841       iobj_0->BoardCoords->data[0] = 0.0;
 5842       i4 = iobj_0->BoardCoords->size[0] * iobj_0->BoardCoords->size[1] *
 5843         iobj_0->BoardCoords->size[2];
 5844       iobj_0->BoardCoords->size[0] = 3;
 5845       iobj_0->BoardCoords->size[1] = 3;
 5846       iobj_0->BoardCoords->size[2] = 2;
 5847       emxEnsureCapacity_real_T1(iobj_0->BoardCoords, i4);
 5848       for (i4 = 0; i4 < 18; i4++) {
 5849         iobj_0->BoardCoords->data[i4] = 0.0;
 5850       }
 5851

 5853       iobj_1->Energy = ((real32_T)rtInf);

 5855       i4 = iobj_1->BoardIdx->size[0] * iobj_1->BoardIdx->size[1];
 5856       iobj_1->BoardIdx->size[0] = 1;
 5857       iobj_1->BoardIdx->size[1] = 1;
 5858       emxEnsureCapacity_real_T(iobj_1->BoardIdx, i4);

 5860       i4 = iobj_1->BoardIdx->size[0] * iobj_1->BoardIdx->size[1];
 5861       iobj_1->BoardIdx->size[0] = 3;
 5862       iobj_1->BoardIdx->size[1] = 3;
 5863       emxEnsureCapacity_real_T(iobj_1->BoardIdx, i4);
 5864       for (i4 = 0; i4 < 9; i4++) {
 5865         iobj_1->BoardIdx->data[i4] = 0.0;
 5866       }
 5867   
 5868       i4 = iobj_1->BoardCoords->size[0] * iobj_1->BoardCoords->size[1] *
 5869         iobj_1->BoardCoords->size[2];
 5870       iobj_1->BoardCoords->size[0] = 1;
 5871       iobj_1->BoardCoords->size[1] = 1;
 5872       iobj_1->BoardCoords->size[2] = 1;
 5873       emxEnsureCapacity_real_T1(iobj_1->BoardCoords, i4);
 5874       iobj_1->BoardCoords->data[0] = 0.0;

 5881       for (i4 = 0; i4 < 18; i4++) {

 5886       emxInit_real_T1(&b_currentBoard, 2);
 5887       emxInit_real_T(&c_currentBoard, 3);

 5895           b_seedIdx->data[b_seedIdx->size[0] * i4] = (unsigned int)seedIdx->

 5900         for (i4 = 0; i4 < 2; i4++) {

 5902         }
 5903   
 5904         cornerOrientations(Ix2, Iy2, Ixy, c_x, v1, v2);
 5905         if ((std::abs(std::abs(std::abs(rt_atan2f_snf(v1[1], v1[0])) - 3.14159274F)

 5907               (std::abs(rt_atan2f_snf(v2[1], v2[0])) - 3.14159274F) - (float)theta)
 5908              > 0.58904862254808621)) {
 5909         } else {
 5910           Checkerboard_initialize(currentBoard, (double)(unsigned int)
 5911             seedIdx->data[i], points, v1, v2);
 5912           if (currentBoard->isValid) {
 5913             hasExpanded = true;
 5914             while (hasExpanded) {
 5915               currentBoard->PreviousEnergy = currentBoard->Energy;
 5916               b_i = 0;
 5917               do {
 5918                 exitg1 = 0;
 5919                 if (b_i < 4) {

 5925                       exitg1 = 1;
 5926                     } else {

 5928                       switch ((int)currentBoard->LastExpandDirection) {
 5929                        case 1:

 5932                           i5 = 0;

 5935                           i5 = 1;
 5936                         }
 5937   
 5938                         b_x = currentBoard->BoardIdx->size[1];
 5939                         i6 = b_currentBoard->size[0] * b_currentBoard->size[1];

 5942                         emxEnsureCapacity_real_T(b_currentBoard, i6);
 5943                         for (i6 = 0; i6 < b_x; i6++) {
 5944                           loop_ub = i4 - i5;
 5945                           for (b_loop_ub = 0; b_loop_ub < loop_ub; b_loop_ub++) {
 5946                             b_currentBoard->data[b_loop_ub + b_currentBoard->size
 5947                               [0] * i6] = currentBoard->BoardIdx->data[(i5 +
 5948                               b_loop_ub) + currentBoard->BoardIdx->size[0] * i6];
 5949                           }
 5950                         }
 5951   
 5952                         i4 = currentBoard->BoardIdx->size[0] *

 6346   
 6347   static void imfilter(emxArray_real32_T *varargin_1)
 6348   {
 6349     int finalSize_idx_0;
 6350     double pad[2];
 6351     int finalSize_idx_1;
 6352     emxArray_real32_T *a;
 6353     emxArray_real_T *b_a;
 6354     int r;
 6355     int iC;
 6356     emxArray_real_T *result;
 6357     int iv2[2];
 6358     boolean_T b1;
 6359     int cEnd;
 6360     int cEnd1;
 6361     int ma;
 6362     int na;
 6363     int cidx;
 6364     int lastColB;
 6365     int iA;
 6366     int lastColA;
 6367     int k;
 6368     int firstRowA;
 6369     int aidx;
 6370     int iB;
 6371     int i;
 6372     int b_i;
 6373     int a_length;
 6374     finalSize_idx_0 = varargin_1->size[0];
 6375     pad[0] = 1.0;
 6376     finalSize_idx_1 = varargin_1->size[1];
 6377     pad[1] = 0.0;
 6378     if (!((varargin_1->size[0] == 0) || (varargin_1->size[1] == 0))) {
 6379       emxInit_real32_T(&a, 2);
 6380       emxInit_real_T1(&b_a, 2);
 6381       padImage(varargin_1, pad, a);
 6382       r = b_a->size[0] * b_a->size[1];
 6383       b_a->size[0] = a->size[0];
 6384       b_a->size[1] = a->size[1];
 6385       emxEnsureCapacity_real_T(b_a, r);
 6386       iC = a->size[0] * a->size[1];
 6387       for (r = 0; r < iC; r++) {
 6388         b_a->data[r] = a->data[r];
 6389       }
 6390   
 6391       emxFree_real32_T(&a);
 6392       for (r = 0; r < 2; r++) {
 6393         iv2[r] = b_a->size[r];
 6394       }
 6395   
 6396       emxInit_real_T1(&result, 2);
 6397       r = result->size[0] * result->size[1];
 6398       result->size[0] = iv2[0];
 6399       result->size[1] = iv2[1];
 6400       emxEnsureCapacity_real_T(result, r);
 6401       iC = iv2[0] * iv2[1];
 6402       for (r = 0; r < iC; r++) {
 6403         result->data[r] = 0.0;
 6404       }
 6405   
 6406       if ((b_a->size[1] == 0) || (iv2[1] == 0)) {
 6407         b1 = true;
 6408       } else {
 6409         b1 = false;
 6410       }
 6411   
 6412       if (!b1) {
 6413         cEnd = iv2[1];
 6414         cEnd1 = iv2[0];
 6415         ma = b_a->size[0];
 6416         na = b_a->size[1];
 6417         if (1 <= iv2[1] - 1) {
 6418           lastColB = 1;
 6419         } else {
 6420           lastColB = iv2[1];
 6421         }
 6422   
 6423         iA = 0;
 6424         while (iA <= lastColB - 1) {
 6425           if (na - 1 < cEnd - 1) {
 6426             lastColA = na;
 6427           } else {
 6428             lastColA = cEnd;
 6429           }
 6430   
 6431           for (k = 0; k < lastColA; k++) {
 6432             if (k > 0) {
 6433               firstRowA = k;
 6434             } else {
 6435               firstRowA = 0;
 6436             }
 6437   
 6438             iC = firstRowA * cEnd1;
 6439             iA = k * ma;
 6440             iB = 0;
 6441             for (i = 0; i < 3; i++) {
 6442               firstRowA = (i < 1);
 6443               if (i + ma <= cEnd1) {
 6444                 b_i = ma;
 6445               } else {
 6446                 b_i = (cEnd1 - i) + 1;
 6447               }
 6448   
 6449               a_length = b_i - firstRowA;
 6450               aidx = iA + firstRowA;
 6451               cidx = iC;
 6452               for (r = 1; r <= a_length; r++) {
 6453                 result->data[cidx] += (-1.0 + (double)iB) * b_a->data[aidx];
 6454                 aidx++;
 6455                 cidx++;
 6456               }
 6457   
 6458               iB++;
 6459               if (i >= 1) {
 6460                 iC++;
 6461               }
 6462             }
 6463           }
 6464   
 6465           iA = 1;
 6466         }
 6467       }
 6468   
 6469       emxFree_real_T(&b_a);
 6470       if (2.0 > (double)finalSize_idx_0 + 1.0) {
 6471         r = 0;
 6472         cidx = 0;
 6473       } else {
 6474         r = 1;
 6475         cidx = finalSize_idx_0 + 1;
 6476       }
 6477   
 6478       if (1 > finalSize_idx_1) {
 6479         iC = 0;
 6480       } else {
 6481         iC = finalSize_idx_1;
 6482       }
 6483   
 6484       iA = varargin_1->size[0] * varargin_1->size[1];
 6485       varargin_1->size[0] = cidx - r;
 6486       varargin_1->size[1] = iC;

 6490         for (aidx = 0; aidx < firstRowA; aidx++) {

 6492             [(r + aidx) + result->size[0] * iA];
 6493         }
 6494       }
 6495   
 6496       emxFree_real_T(&result);
 6497     }
 6498   }

 7711               while ((!exitg1) && (indx <= b_y * r - 1)) {
 7712                 if (b_imnh_data[indx] > b_pixel) {
 7713                   continuePropagation = false;
 7714                   exitg1 = true;
 7715                 } else if ((b_imnh_data[indx] == b_pixel) && (!fparams.bw->
 7716                             data[c_imnhInds_data[indx] - 1])) {
 7717                   continuePropagation = false;
 7718                   exitg1 = true;
 7719                 } else {
 7720                   indx++;
 7721                 }
 7722               }
 7723             }
 7724   
 7725             BW->data[pind] = continuePropagation;
 7726           }
 7727         }
 7728   
 7729         secondIndRange[0] = nhoodObj->InteriorEnd[0] + 1;
 7730         secondIndRange[1] = nhoodObj->ImageSize[0];
 7731         pixelsPerImPage[1] = nhoodObj->ImageSize[1];
 7732         padValue = (float)nhoodObj->PadValue;
 7733         u0 = secondIndRange[0];
 7734         if (!(u0 > 1)) {
 7735           u0 = 1;
 7736         }
 7737   
 7738         varargin_2 = nhoodObj->ImageSize[0];
 7739         indx = secondIndRange[1];
 7740         if (indx < varargin_2) {
 7741           varargin_2 = indx;
 7742         }
 7743   
 7744         b_varargin_2 = nhoodObj->ImageSize[1];
 7745         indx = pixelsPerImPage[1];
 7746         if (indx < b_varargin_2) {
 7747           b_varargin_2 = indx;
 7748         }
 7749   
 7750         for (b_secondInd = 1; b_secondInd <= b_varargin_2; b_secondInd++) {
 7751           for (firstInd = u0; firstInd <= varargin_2; firstInd++) {
 7752             indx = nhoodObj->ImageSize[0];
 7753             pind = ((b_secondInd - 1) * indx + firstInd) - 1;
 7754             for (i = 0; i < 9; i++) {
 7755               imnhInds_[i] = nhoodObj->ImageNeighborLinearOffsets[i];
 7756             }
 7757   
 7758             for (i = 0; i < 9; i++) {
 7759               imnhInds_[i] = (imnhInds_[i] + pind) + 1;
 7760             }
 7761   
 7762             for (i = 0; i < 2; i++) {
 7763               b_centerPixelSub[i] = nhoodObj->ImageSize[i];
 7764             }
 7765   
 7766             if (b_centerPixelSub[0] == 0) {
 7767               r = 0;
 7768             } else {
 7769               r = pind - b_centerPixelSub[0] * div_s32(pind, b_centerPixelSub[0]);
 7770             }
 7771   
 7772             k = pind - r;
 7773             if (b_centerPixelSub[0] == 0) {
 7774               if (k == 0) {
 7775                 b_y = 0;
 7776               } else if (k < 0) {
 7777                 b_y = MIN_int32_T;
 7778               } else {
 7779                 b_y = MAX_int32_T;
 7780               }
 7781             } else if (b_centerPixelSub[0] == 1) {
 7782               b_y = k;
 7783             } else if (b_centerPixelSub[0] == -1) {
 7784               b_y = -k;
 7785             } else {
 7786               if (k >= 0) {
 7787                 indx = k;
 7788               } else if (k == MIN_int32_T) {
 7789                 indx = MAX_int32_T;
 7790               } else {
 7791                 indx = -k;
 7792               }
 7793   
 7794               if (b_centerPixelSub[0] >= 0) {
 7795                 i = b_centerPixelSub[0];
 7796               } else if (b_centerPixelSub[0] == MIN_int32_T) {
 7797                 i = MAX_int32_T;
 7798               } else {
 7799                 i = -b_centerPixelSub[0];
 7800               }
 7801   
 7802               b_y = div_s32(indx, i);
 7803               indx -= b_y * i;
 7804               if ((indx > 0) && (indx >= (i >> 1) + (i & 1))) {
 7805                 b_y++;
 7806               }
 7807   
 7808               if ((k < 0) != (b_centerPixelSub[0] < 0)) {
 7809                 b_y = -b_y;
 7810               }
 7811             }
 7812   
 7813             e_pixelSub[1] = b_y + 1;
 7814             e_pixelSub[0] = r + 1;
 7815             for (i = 0; i < 2; i++) {
 7816               pixelSub[i] = e_pixelSub[i];
 7817             }
 7818   
 7819             for (i = 0; i < 18; i++) {
 7820               a[i] = nhoodObj->NeighborSubscriptOffsets[i];
 7821             }
 7822   
 7823             for (indx = 0; indx < 2; indx++) {
 7824               for (k = 0; k < 9; k++) {
 7825                 imnhSubs[k + 9 * indx] = a[k + 9 * indx] + pixelSub[indx];
 7826               }
 7827             }
 7828   
 7829             for (i = 0; i < 9; i++) {
 7830               nhConn[i] = true;
 7831             }
 7832   
 7833             switch ((int)nhoodObj->Padding) {
 7834              case 1:
 7835               for (b_y = 0; b_y < 9; b_y++) {
 7836                 k = 0;
 7837                 exitg1 = false;
 7838                 while ((!exitg1) && (k < 2)) {
 7839                   if ((imnhSubs[b_y + 9 * k] < 1) || (imnhSubs[b_y + 9 * k] >
 7840                        nhoodObj->ImageSize[k])) {
 7841                     nhConn[b_y] = false;
 7842                     exitg1 = true;
 7843                   } else {
 7844                     k++;
 7845                   }
 7846                 }
 7847               }
 7848   
 7849               d_trueCount = 0;
 7850               for (i = 0; i < 9; i++) {
 7851                 if (nhConn[i]) {
 7852                   d_trueCount++;
 7853                 }
 7854               }
 7855   
 7856               indx = 0;
 7857               for (i = 0; i < 9; i++) {
 7858                 if (nhConn[i]) {
 7859                   d_imnhInds_data[indx] = imnhInds_[i];
 7860                   indx++;
 7861                 }
 7862               }
 7863               break;
 7864   
 7865              case 2:
 7866               d_trueCount = 9;
 7867               for (i = 0; i < 9; i++) {
 7868                 d_imnhInds_data[i] = imnhInds_[i];
 7869               }
 7870   
 7871               for (b_y = 0; b_y < 9; b_y++) {
 7872                 k = 0;
 7873                 exitg1 = false;
 7874                 while ((!exitg1) && (k < 2)) {
 7875                   if ((imnhSubs[b_y + 9 * k] < 1) || (imnhSubs[b_y + 9 * k] >
 7876                        nhoodObj->ImageSize[k])) {
 7877                     nhConn[b_y] = false;
 7878                     d_imnhInds_data[b_y] = 1;
 7879                     exitg1 = true;
 7880                   } else {
 7881                     k++;
 7882                   }
 7883                 }
 7884               }
 7885               break;
 7886   
 7887              case 3:
 7888               d_trueCount = 9;
 7889               for (i = 0; i < 9; i++) {
 7890                 d_imnhInds_data[i] = imnhInds_[i];
 7891               }
 7892   
 7893               for (b_y = 0; b_y < 9; b_y++) {
 7894                 for (i = 0; i < 2; i++) {
 7895                   pixelSub[i] = imnhSubs[b_y + 9 * i];
 7896                 }
 7897   
 7898                 for (k = 0; k < 2; k++) {
 7899                   i = pixelSub[k];
 7900                   if (pixelSub[k] < 1) {
 7901                     nhConn[b_y] = false;
 7902                     i = 1;
 7903                   }
 7904   
 7905                   if (i > nhoodObj->ImageSize[k]) {
 7906                     nhConn[b_y] = false;
 7907                     i = nhoodObj->ImageSize[k];
 7908                   }
 7909   
 7910                   pixelSub[k] = i;
 7911                 }
 7912   
 7913                 if (!nhConn[b_y]) {
 7914                   for (i = 0; i < 2; i++) {
 7915                     b_centerPixelSub[i] = nhoodObj->ImageSize[i];
 7916                   }
 7917   
 7918                   b_k[0] = 1;
 7919                   b_k[1] = b_centerPixelSub[0];
 7920                   indx = 1;
 7921                   for (i = 0; i < 2; i++) {
 7922                     indx += (pixelSub[i] - 1) * b_k[i];
 7923                   }
 7924   
 7925                   d_imnhInds_data[b_y] = indx;
 7926                 }
 7927               }
 7928               break;
 7929   
 7930              case 4:
 7931               d_trueCount = 9;
 7932               for (i = 0; i < 9; i++) {
 7933                 d_imnhInds_data[i] = imnhInds_[i];
 7934               }
 7935   
 7936               for (b_y = 0; b_y < 9; b_y++) {
 7937                 for (i = 0; i < 2; i++) {
 7938                   pixelSub[i] = imnhSubs[b_y + 9 * i];
 7939                 }
 7940   
 7941                 for (k = 0; k < 2; k++) {
 7942                   i = pixelSub[k];
 7943                   if (pixelSub[k] < 1) {
 7944                     nhConn[b_y] = false;
 7945                     indx = nhoodObj->ImageSize[k];
 7946                     i = pixelSub[k] + (indx << 1);
 7947                   }
 7948   
 7949                   if (i > nhoodObj->ImageSize[k]) {
 7950                     nhConn[b_y] = false;
 7951                     indx = nhoodObj->ImageSize[k];
 7952                     i = ((indx << 1) - i) + 1;
 7953                   }
 7954   
 7955                   pixelSub[k] = i;
 7956                 }
 7957   
 7958                 if (!nhConn[b_y]) {
 7959                   for (i = 0; i < 2; i++) {
 7960                     b_centerPixelSub[i] = nhoodObj->ImageSize[i];
 7961                   }
 7962   
 7963                   b_k[0] = 1;
 7964                   b_k[1] = b_centerPixelSub[0];
 7965                   indx = 1;
 7966                   for (i = 0; i < 2; i++) {
 7967                     indx += (pixelSub[i] - 1) * b_k[i];
 7968                   }
 7969   
 7970                   d_imnhInds_data[b_y] = indx;
 7971                 }
 7972               }
 7973               break;
 7974             }
 7975   
 7976             continuePropagation = (in->size[0] == 1);
 7977             if (continuePropagation) {
 7978               if (0 <= d_trueCount - 1) {
 7979                 memcpy(&tmp_data[0], &d_imnhInds_data[0], (unsigned int)
 7980                        (d_trueCount * (int)sizeof(int)));
 7981               }
 7982   
 7983               b_y = 1;
 7984               r = d_trueCount;
 7985               for (i = 0; i < d_trueCount; i++) {
 7986                 b_imnh_data[i] = in->data[tmp_data[i] - 1];
 7987               }
 7988             } else {
 7989               b_y = d_trueCount;
 7990               r = 1;
 7991               for (i = 0; i < d_trueCount; i++) {
 7992                 b_imnh_data[i] = in->data[d_imnhInds_data[i] - 1];
 7993               }
 7994             }
 7995   
 7996             if (nhoodObj->Padding == 2.0) {
 7997               k = 0;
 7998               for (i = 0; i < 9; i++) {
 7999                 if (!nhConn[i]) {
 8000                   k++;
 8001                 }
 8002               }
 8003   
 8004               indx = 0;
 8005               for (i = 0; i < 9; i++) {
 8006                 if (!nhConn[i]) {
 8007                   e_tmp_data[indx] = i + 1;
 8008                   indx++;
 8009                 }
 8010               }
 8011   
 8012               for (i = 0; i < k; i++) {
 8013                 b_imnh_data[e_tmp_data[i] - 1] = padValue;
 8014               }
 8015             }
 8016   
 8017             b_pixel = in->data[pind];
 8018             continuePropagation = fparams.bw->data[pind];
 8019             if (fparams.bw->data[pind]) {
 8020               indx = 0;
 8021               exitg1 = false;
 8022               while ((!exitg1) && (indx <= b_y * r - 1)) {
 8023                 if (b_imnh_data[indx] > b_pixel) {
 8024                   continuePropagation = false;
 8025                   exitg1 = true;
 8026                 } else if ((b_imnh_data[indx] == b_pixel) && (!fparams.bw->
 8027                             data[d_imnhInds_data[indx] - 1])) {
 8028                   continuePropagation = false;
 8029                   exitg1 = true;
 8030                 } else {
 8031                   indx++;
 8032                 }
 8033               }
 8034             }
 8035   
 8036             BW->data[pind] = continuePropagation;
 8037           }
 8038         }
 8039       }
 8040   
 8041       continuePropagation = !isequal(bwpre, BW);
 8042     }
 8043   
 8044     emxFreeStruct_struct_T(&fparams);
 8045     emxFree_real32_T(&in);
 8046     emxFree_boolean_T(&imParams_bw);
 8047     emxFree_boolean_T(&bwpre);
 8048     emxFree_boolean_T(&out_);
 8049   }

 8051   static boolean_T isequal(const emxArray_boolean_T *varargin_1, const
 8052     emxArray_boolean_T *varargin_2)
 8053   {
 8054     boolean_T p;
 8055     boolean_T b_p;
 8056     int k;
 8057     boolean_T exitg1;
 8058     p = false;
 8059     b_p = false;
 8060     if ((varargin_1->size[0] != varargin_2->size[0]) || (varargin_1->size[1] !=
 8061          varargin_2->size[1])) {
 8062     } else {
 8063       b_p = true;
 8064     }
 8065   
 8066     if (b_p && (!((varargin_1->size[0] == 0) || (varargin_1->size[1] == 0))) &&
 8067         (!((varargin_2->size[0] == 0) || (varargin_2->size[1] == 0)))) {
 8068       k = 0;
 8069       exitg1 = false;
 8070       while ((!exitg1) && (k <= varargin_2->size[0] * varargin_2->size[1] - 1)) {
 8071         if (varargin_1->data[k] != varargin_2->data[k]) {
 8072           b_p = false;
 8073           exitg1 = true;
 8074         } else {
 8075           k++;
 8076         }
 8077       }
 8078     }
 8079   
 8080     if (b_p) {
 8081       p = true;
 8082     }
 8083   
 8084     return p;
 8085   }

 8087   static boolean_T isrow(const emxArray_real32_T *x)
 8088   {
 8089     return x->size[0] == 1;
 8090   }
 8091   
 8092   static float mean(const emxArray_real32_T *x)
 8093   {
 8094     float y;
 8095     int firstBlockLength;
 8096     int nblocks;
 8097     int lastBlockLength;
 8098     int k;
 8099     int xblockoffset;
 8100     float bsum;
 8101     int hi;
 8102     if (x->size[0] == 0) {
 8103       y = 0.0F;
 8104     } else {
 8105       if (x->size[0] <= 1024) {
 8106         firstBlockLength = x->size[0];
 8107         lastBlockLength = 0;
 8108         nblocks = 1;
 8109       } else {
 8110         firstBlockLength = 1024;
 8111         nblocks = x->size[0] / 1024;
 8112         lastBlockLength = x->size[0] - (nblocks << 10);
 8113         if (lastBlockLength > 0) {
 8114           nblocks++;
 8115         } else {
 8116           lastBlockLength = 1024;
 8117         }
 8118       }
 8119   
 8120       y = x->data[0];
 8121       for (k = 2; k <= firstBlockLength; k++) {
 8122         y += x->data[k - 1];
 8123       }
 8124   
 8125       for (firstBlockLength = 2; firstBlockLength <= nblocks; firstBlockLength++)
 8126       {
 8127         xblockoffset = (firstBlockLength - 1) << 10;
 8128         bsum = x->data[xblockoffset];
 8129         if (firstBlockLength == nblocks) {
 8130           hi = lastBlockLength;
 8131         } else {
 8132           hi = 1024;
 8133         }
 8134   
 8135         for (k = 2; k <= hi; k++) {
 8136           bsum += x->data[(xblockoffset + k) - 1];
 8137         }
 8138   
 8139         y += bsum;
 8140       }
 8141     }
 8142   
 8143     y /= (float)x->size[0];
 8144     return y;
 8145   }
 8146   
 8147   static void merge(emxArray_int32_T *idx, emxArray_real32_T *x, int offset, int
 8148                     np, int nq, emxArray_int32_T *iwork, emxArray_real32_T *xwork)
 8149   {
 8150     int n;
 8151     int qend;
 8152     int p;
 8153     int iout;
 8154     int exitg1;
 8155     if (nq != 0) {
 8156       n = np + nq;
 8157       for (qend = 0; qend + 1 <= n; qend++) {
 8158         iwork->data[qend] = idx->data[offset + qend];
 8159         xwork->data[qend] = x->data[offset + qend];
 8160       }
 8161   
 8162       p = 0;
 8163       n = np;
 8164       qend = np + nq;
 8165       iout = offset - 1;
 8166       do {
 8167         exitg1 = 0;
 8168         iout++;
 8169         if (xwork->data[p] >= xwork->data[n]) {
 8170           idx->data[iout] = iwork->data[p];
 8171           x->data[iout] = xwork->data[p];
 8172           if (p + 1 < np) {
 8173             p++;
 8174           } else {
 8175             exitg1 = 1;
 8176           }
 8177         } else {
 8178           idx->data[iout] = iwork->data[n];
 8179           x->data[iout] = xwork->data[n];
 8180           if (n + 1 < qend) {
 8181             n++;
 8182           } else {
 8183             n = (iout - p) + 1;
 8184             while (p + 1 <= np) {
 8185               idx->data[n + p] = iwork->data[p];
 8186               x->data[n + p] = xwork->data[p];
 8187               p++;
 8188             }
 8189   
 8190             exitg1 = 1;
 8191           }
 8192         }
 8193       } while (exitg1 == 0);
 8194     }
 8195   }
 8196   
 8197   static void merge_block(emxArray_int32_T *idx, emxArray_real32_T *x, int offset,
 8198     int n, int preSortLevel, emxArray_int32_T *iwork, emxArray_real32_T *xwork)
 8199   {
 8200     int nPairs;
 8201     int bLen;
 8202     int tailOffset;
 8203     int nTail;
 8204     nPairs = n >> preSortLevel;
 8205     bLen = 1 << preSortLevel;
 8206     while (nPairs > 1) {
 8207       if ((nPairs & 1) != 0) {
 8208         nPairs--;
 8209         tailOffset = bLen * nPairs;
 8210         nTail = n - tailOffset;
 8211         if (nTail > bLen) {
 8212           merge(idx, x, offset + tailOffset, bLen, nTail - bLen, iwork, xwork);
 8213         }
 8214       }
 8215   
 8216       tailOffset = bLen << 1;
 8217       nPairs >>= 1;
 8218       for (nTail = 1; nTail <= nPairs; nTail++) {
 8219         merge(idx, x, offset + (nTail - 1) * tailOffset, bLen, bLen, iwork, xwork);
 8220       }
 8221   
 8222       bLen = tailOffset;
 8223     }
 8224   
 8225     if (n > bLen) {
 8226       merge(idx, x, offset, bLen, n - bLen, iwork, xwork);
 8227     }
 8228   }
 8229   
 8230   static double norm(const emxArray_real_T *x)
 8231   {
 8232     double y;
 8233     double scale;
 8234     int k;
 8235     double absxk;
 8236     double t;
 8237     if (x->size[0] == 0) {
 8238       y = 0.0;
 8239     } else {
 8240       y = 0.0;
 8241       if (x->size[0] == 1) {
 8242         y = std::abs(x->data[0]);
 8243       } else {
 8244         scale = 3.3121686421112381E-170;
 8245         for (k = 1; k <= x->size[0]; k++) {
 8246           absxk = std::abs(x->data[k - 1]);
 8247           if (absxk > scale) {
 8248             t = scale / absxk;
 8249             y = 1.0 + y * t * t;
 8250             scale = absxk;
 8251           } else {
 8252             t = absxk / scale;
 8253             y += t * t;
 8254           }
 8255         }
 8256   
 8257         y = scale * std::sqrt(y);
 8258       }
 8259     }
 8260   
 8261     return y;
 8262   }

 8264   static void orient(c_vision_internal_calibration_c **board, const
 8265                      emxArray_real32_T *I)
 8266   {
 8267     float x;
 8268     emxArray_real_T *b_board;
 8269     emxArray_boolean_T *upperLeftMask;
 8270     emxArray_boolean_T *nextSquareMask;
 8271     int j;
 8272     double upperLeftPolyX[4];
 8273     int i1;
 8274     double upperLeftPolyY[4];
 8275     int k;
 8276     emxArray_real_T *newBoardCoords1;
 8277     int vspread;
 8278     emxArray_int32_T *r50;
 8279     emxArray_real_T *newBoardCoords2;
 8280     emxArray_real_T *r51;
 8281     emxArray_int32_T *r52;
 8282     emxArray_real32_T *b_I;
 8283     float b_x;
 8284     c_vision_internal_calibration_c *r53;
 8285     boolean_T s;
 8286     boolean_T t;
 8287     emxArray_real_T *r54;
 8288     emxArray_real_T *r55;
 8289     emxArray_boolean_T *c_x;
 8290     int ix;
 8291     boolean_T exitg1;
 8292     x = (*board)->Energy;
 8293     if (!rtIsInfF(x)) {
 8294       if ((*board)->BoardCoords->size[0] < (*board)->BoardCoords->size[1]) {
 8295         emxInit_real_T1(&b_board, 2);
 8296         rot90((*board)->BoardIdx, b_board);
 8297         j = (*board)->BoardIdx->size[0] * (*board)->BoardIdx->size[1];
 8298         (*board)->BoardIdx->size[0] = b_board->size[0];
 8299         (*board)->BoardIdx->size[1] = b_board->size[1];
 8300         emxEnsureCapacity_real_T((*board)->BoardIdx, j);
 8301         i1 = b_board->size[0] * b_board->size[1];
 8302         for (j = 0; j < i1; j++) {
 8303           (*board)->BoardIdx->data[j] = b_board->data[j];
 8304         }
 8305   
 8306         i1 = (*board)->BoardCoords->size[0];
 8307         k = (*board)->BoardCoords->size[1];
 8308         j = b_board->size[0] * b_board->size[1];
 8309         b_board->size[0] = i1;
 8310         b_board->size[1] = k;
 8311         emxEnsureCapacity_real_T(b_board, j);
 8312         for (j = 0; j < k; j++) {
 8313           for (vspread = 0; vspread < i1; vspread++) {
 8314             b_board->data[vspread + b_board->size[0] * j] = (*board)->
 8315               BoardCoords->data[vspread + (*board)->BoardCoords->size[0] * j];
 8316           }
 8317         }
 8318   
 8319         emxInit_real_T1(&newBoardCoords1, 2);
 8320         rot90(b_board, newBoardCoords1);
 8321         i1 = (*board)->BoardCoords->size[0];
 8322         k = (*board)->BoardCoords->size[1];
 8323         j = b_board->size[0] * b_board->size[1];
 8324         b_board->size[0] = i1;
 8325         b_board->size[1] = k;
 8326         emxEnsureCapacity_real_T(b_board, j);
 8327         for (j = 0; j < k; j++) {
 8328           for (vspread = 0; vspread < i1; vspread++) {
 8329             b_board->data[vspread + b_board->size[0] * j] = (*board)->
 8330               BoardCoords->data[(vspread + (*board)->BoardCoords->size[0] * j) + (*
 8331               board)->BoardCoords->size[0] * (*board)->BoardCoords->size[1]];
 8332           }
 8333         }
 8334

 8675     ztemp->size[0] = (int)uv1[0];

 8679     y->size[0] = (int)uv1[0];
 8680     y->size[1] = (int)uv1[1];

 8683     k = 0;

 8705   static void rot90(const emxArray_real_T *A, emxArray_real_T *B)
 8706   {
 8707     int n;
 8708     int sizeB_idx_0;
 8709     int sizeB_idx_1;
 8710     int A_idx_0;
 8711     int B_idx_0;
 8712     n = A->size[1];
 8713     sizeB_idx_0 = A->size[1];
 8714     sizeB_idx_1 = A->size[0];
 8715     A_idx_0 = B->size[0] * B->size[1];
 8716     B->size[0] = sizeB_idx_0;
 8717     B->size[1] = sizeB_idx_1;
 8718     emxEnsureCapacity_real_T(B, A_idx_0);
 8719     for (sizeB_idx_0 = 1; sizeB_idx_0 <= n; sizeB_idx_0++) {
 8720       for (sizeB_idx_1 = 0; sizeB_idx_1 + 1 <= A->size[0]; sizeB_idx_1++) {
 8721         A_idx_0 = A->size[0];
 8722         B_idx_0 = B->size[0];
 8723         B->data[(sizeB_idx_0 + B_idx_0 * sizeB_idx_1) - 1] = A->data[sizeB_idx_1 +
 8724           A_idx_0 * (n - sizeB_idx_0)];
 8725       }
 8726     }
 8727   }

 8800   static float rt_atan2f_snf(float u0, float u1)
 8801   {
 8802     float y;
 8803     int b_u0;
 8804     int b_u1;
 8805     if (rtIsNaNF(u0) || rtIsNaNF(u1)) {
 8806       y = ((real32_T)rtNaN);
 8807     } else if (rtIsInfF(u0) && rtIsInfF(u1)) {
 8808       if (u0 > 0.0F) {
 8809         b_u0 = 1;
 8810       } else {
 8811         b_u0 = -1;
 8812       }
 8813   
 8814       if (u1 > 0.0F) {
 8815         b_u1 = 1;
 8816       } else {
 8817         b_u1 = -1;
 8818       }
 8819   
 8820       y = std::atan2((float)b_u0, (float)b_u1);
 8821     } else if (u1 == 0.0F) {
 8822       if (u0 > 0.0F) {
 8823         y = RT_PIF / 2.0F;
 8824       } else if (u0 < 0.0F) {
 8825         y = -(RT_PIF / 2.0F);
 8826       } else {
 8827         y = 0.0F;
 8828       }
 8829     } else {
 8830       y = std::atan2(u0, u1);
 8831     }
 8832   
 8833     return y;
 8834   }

 8836   static double rt_hypotd_snf(double u0, double u1)
 8837   {
 8838     double y;
 8839     double a;
 8840     double b;
 8841     a = std::abs(u0);
 8842     b = std::abs(u1);
 8843     if (a < b) {
 8844       a /= b;
 8845       y = b * std::sqrt(a * a + 1.0);
 8846     } else if (a > b) {
 8847       b /= a;
 8848       y = a * std::sqrt(b * b + 1.0);
 8849     } else if (rtIsNaN(b)) {
 8850       y = b;
 8851     } else {
 8852       y = a * 1.4142135623730951;
 8853     }
 8854   
 8855     return y;
 8856   }
 8857   
 8858   static float rt_hypotf_snf(float u0, float u1)
 8859   {
 8860     float y;
 8861     float a;
 8862     float b;
 8863     a = std::abs(u0);
 8864     b = std::abs(u1);
 8865     if (a < b) {
 8866       a /= b;
 8867       y = b * std::sqrt(a * a + 1.0F);
 8868     } else if (a > b) {
 8869       b /= a;
 8870       y = a * std::sqrt(b * b + 1.0F);
 8871     } else if (rtIsNaNF(b)) {
 8872       y = b;
 8873     } else {
 8874       y = a * 1.41421354F;
 8875     }
 8876   
 8877     return y;
 8878   }
 8879   
 8880   static double rt_remd_snf(double u0, double u1)
 8881   {
 8882     double y;
 8883     double b_u1;
 8884     double q;
 8885     if (!((!rtIsNaN(u0)) && (!rtIsInf(u0)) && ((!rtIsNaN(u1)) && (!rtIsInf(u1)))))
 8886     {
 8887       y = rtNaN;
 8888     } else {
 8889       if (u1 < 0.0) {
 8890         b_u1 = std::ceil(u1);
 8891       } else {
 8892         b_u1 = std::floor(u1);
 8893       }
 8894   
 8895       if ((u1 != 0.0) && (u1 != b_u1)) {
 8896         q = std::abs(u0 / u1);
 8897         if (std::abs(q - std::floor(q + 0.5)) <= DBL_EPSILON * q) {
 8898           y = 0.0 * u0;
 8899         } else {
 8900           y = std::fmod(u0, u1);
 8901         }
 8902       } else {
 8903         y = std::fmod(u0, u1);
 8904       }
 8905     }
 8906   
 8907     return y;
 8908   }
 8909   
 8910   static double rt_roundd_snf(double u)
 8911   {
 8912     double y;
 8913     if (std::abs(u) < 4.503599627370496E+15) {
 8914       if (u >= 0.5) {
 8915         y = std::floor(u + 0.5);
 8916       } else if (u > -0.5) {
 8917         y = u * 0.0;
 8918       } else {
 8919         y = std::ceil(u - 0.5);
 8920       }
 8921     } else {
 8922       y = u;
 8923     }
 8924   
 8925     return y;
 8926   }
