 9279       b_a->data[ma] = r1->data[ma] - r2->data[ma];
 9280     }
 9281   
 9282     firstRowA = b_a->size[0] * b_a->size[1] - 1;
 9283     aidx = 0;
 9284     for (i = 0; i <= firstRowA; i++) {
 9285       if (r1->data[i] - r2->data[i] < 0.0F) {
 9286         aidx++;
 9287       }
 9288     }
 9289   
 9290     emxInit_int32_T(&r3, 1);
 9291     ma = r3->size[0];
 9292     r3->size[0] = aidx;
 9293     emxEnsureCapacity_int32_T(r3, ma);
 9294     aidx = 0;
 9295     for (i = 0; i <= firstRowA; i++) {
 9296       if (r1->data[i] - r2->data[i] < 0.0F) {
 9297         r3->data[aidx] = i + 1;
 9298         aidx++;
 9299       }
 9300     }
 9301   
 9302     aidx = r3->size[0];
 9303     for (ma = 0; ma < aidx; ma++) {
 9304       cxy->data[r3->data[ma] - 1] = 0.0F;
 9305     }
 9306   
 9307     emxFree_int32_T(&r3);
 9308     b_abs(I_45_45, r1);
 9309     ma = r1->size[0] * r1->size[1];
 9310     emxEnsureCapacity_real32_T(r1, ma);
 9311     ma = r1->size[0];
 9312     firstRowA = r1->size[1];
 9313     aidx = ma * firstRowA;
 9314     for (ma = 0; ma < aidx; ma++) {
 9315       r1->data[ma] *= 4.0F;
 9316     }
 9317   
 9318     b_abs(Ix, r2);
 9319     b_abs(Iy, a);
 9320     ma = r2->size[0] * r2->size[1];
 9321     emxEnsureCapacity_real32_T(r2, ma);
 9322     ma = r2->size[0];
 9323     firstRowA = r2->size[1];
 9324     aidx = ma * firstRowA;
 9325     for (ma = 0; ma < aidx; ma++) {
 9326       r2->data[ma] = 3.0F * (r2->data[ma] + a->data[ma]);
 9327     }
 9328   
 9329     emxFree_real32_T(&a);
 9330     ma = c45->size[0] * c45->size[1];
 9331     c45->size[0] = r1->size[0];
 9332     c45->size[1] = r1->size[1];
 9333     emxEnsureCapacity_real32_T(c45, ma);
 9334     aidx = r1->size[0] * r1->size[1];
 9335     for (ma = 0; ma < aidx; ma++) {
 9336       c45->data[ma] = r1->data[ma] - r2->data[ma];
 9337     }
 9338   
 9339     ma = b_a->size[0] * b_a->size[1];
 9340     b_a->size[0] = r1->size[0];
 9341     b_a->size[1] = r1->size[1];
 9342     emxEnsureCapacity_real_T(b_a, ma);
 9343     aidx = r1->size[0] * r1->size[1];
 9344     for (ma = 0; ma < aidx; ma++) {
 9345       b_a->data[ma] = r1->data[ma] - r2->data[ma];
 9346     }
 9347   
 9348     firstRowA = b_a->size[0] * b_a->size[1] - 1;
 9349     aidx = 0;
 9350     emxFree_real_T(&b_a);
 9351     for (i = 0; i <= firstRowA; i++) {
 9352       if (r1->data[i] - r2->data[i] < 0.0F) {
 9353         aidx++;
 9354       }
 9355     }
 9356   
 9357     emxInit_int32_T(&r4, 1);
 9358     ma = r4->size[0];
 9359     r4->size[0] = aidx;
 9360     emxEnsureCapacity_int32_T(r4, ma);
 9361     aidx = 0;
 9362     for (i = 0; i <= firstRowA; i++) {
 9363       if (r1->data[i] - r2->data[i] < 0.0F) {
 9364         r4->data[aidx] = i + 1;
 9365         aidx++;
 9366       }
 9367     }
 9368   
 9369     emxFree_real32_T(&r2);
 9370     emxFree_real32_T(&r1);
 9371     aidx = r4->size[0];
 9372     for (ma = 0; ma < aidx; ma++) {
 9373       c45->data[r4->data[ma] - 1] = 0.0F;
 9374     }
 9375   
 9376     emxFree_int32_T(&r4);
 9377   }

 9379   static void sort(emxArray_real32_T *x, emxArray_int32_T *idx)
 9380   {
 9381     int dim;
 9382     dim = 2;
 9383     if (x->size[0] != 1) {
 9384       dim = 1;
 9385     }
 9386   
 9387     b_sort(x, dim, idx);
 9388   }
 9389   
 9390   static void sortIdx(emxArray_real32_T *x, emxArray_int32_T *idx)
 9391   {
 9392     int ib;
 9393     int i;
 9394     int n;
 9395     int b_n;
 9396     emxArray_int32_T *iwork;
 9397     float x4[4];
 9398     int idx4[4];
 9399     emxArray_real32_T *xwork;
 9400     int nNaNs;
 9401     int k;
 9402     int wOffset;
 9403     signed char perm[4];
 9404     int nNonNaN;
 9405     int i3;
 9406     int i4;
 9407     int nBlocks;
 9408     int bLen2;
 9409     int nPairs;
 9410     int b_iwork[256];
 9411     float b_xwork[256];
 9412     int exitg1;
 9413     ib = x->size[0];
 9414     i = idx->size[0];
 9415     idx->size[0] = ib;
 9416     emxEnsureCapacity_int32_T(idx, i);
 9417     for (i = 0; i < ib; i++) {
 9418       idx->data[i] = 0;
 9419     }
 9420   
 9421     n = x->size[0];
 9422     b_n = x->size[0];
 9423     for (i = 0; i < 4; i++) {
 9424       x4[i] = 0.0F;
 9425       idx4[i] = 0;
 9426     }
 9427   
 9428     emxInit_int32_T(&iwork, 1);
 9429     i = iwork->size[0];
 9430     iwork->size[0] = ib;
 9431     emxEnsureCapacity_int32_T(iwork, i);
 9432     for (i = 0; i < ib; i++) {
 9433       iwork->data[i] = 0;
 9434     }
 9435   
 9436     emxInit_real32_T1(&xwork, 1);
 9437     ib = x->size[0];
 9438     i = xwork->size[0];
 9439     xwork->size[0] = ib;
 9440     emxEnsureCapacity_real32_T1(xwork, i);
 9441     for (i = 0; i < ib; i++) {
 9442       xwork->data[i] = 0.0F;
 9443     }
 9444   
 9445     nNaNs = 0;
 9446     ib = 0;
 9447     for (k = 0; k + 1 <= b_n; k++) {
 9448       if (rtIsNaNF(x->data[k])) {
 9449         idx->data[(b_n - nNaNs) - 1] = k + 1;
 9450         xwork->data[(b_n - nNaNs) - 1] = x->data[k];
 9451         nNaNs++;
 9452       } else {
 9453         ib++;
 9454         idx4[ib - 1] = k + 1;
 9455         x4[ib - 1] = x->data[k];
 9456         if (ib == 4) {
 9457           i = k - nNaNs;
 9458           if (x4[0] >= x4[1]) {
 9459             ib = 1;
 9460             wOffset = 2;
 9461           } else {
 9462             ib = 2;
 9463             wOffset = 1;
 9464           }
 9465   
 9466           if (x4[2] >= x4[3]) {
 9467             i3 = 3;
 9468             i4 = 4;
 9469           } else {
 9470             i3 = 4;
 9471             i4 = 3;
 9472           }
 9473   
 9474           if (x4[ib - 1] >= x4[i3 - 1]) {
 9475             if (x4[wOffset - 1] >= x4[i3 - 1]) {
 9476               perm[0] = (signed char)ib;
 9477               perm[1] = (signed char)wOffset;
 9478               perm[2] = (signed char)i3;
 9479               perm[3] = (signed char)i4;
 9480             } else if (x4[wOffset - 1] >= x4[i4 - 1]) {
 9481               perm[0] = (signed char)ib;
 9482               perm[1] = (signed char)i3;
 9483               perm[2] = (signed char)wOffset;
 9484               perm[3] = (signed char)i4;
 9485             } else {
 9486               perm[0] = (signed char)ib;
 9487               perm[1] = (signed char)i3;
 9488               perm[2] = (signed char)i4;
 9489               perm[3] = (signed char)wOffset;
 9490             }
 9491           } else if (x4[ib - 1] >= x4[i4 - 1]) {
 9492             if (x4[wOffset - 1] >= x4[i4 - 1]) {
 9493               perm[0] = (signed char)i3;
 9494               perm[1] = (signed char)ib;
 9495               perm[2] = (signed char)wOffset;
 9496               perm[3] = (signed char)i4;
 9497             } else {
 9498               perm[0] = (signed char)i3;
 9499               perm[1] = (signed char)ib;
 9500               perm[2] = (signed char)i4;
 9501               perm[3] = (signed char)wOffset;
 9502             }
 9503           } else {
 9504             perm[0] = (signed char)i3;
 9505             perm[1] = (signed char)i4;
 9506             perm[2] = (signed char)ib;
 9507             perm[3] = (signed char)wOffset;
 9508           }
 9509   
 9510           idx->data[i - 3] = idx4[perm[0] - 1];
 9511           idx->data[i - 2] = idx4[perm[1] - 1];
 9512           idx->data[i - 1] = idx4[perm[2] - 1];
 9513           idx->data[i] = idx4[perm[3] - 1];
 9514           x->data[i - 3] = x4[perm[0] - 1];
 9515           x->data[i - 2] = x4[perm[1] - 1];
 9516           x->data[i - 1] = x4[perm[2] - 1];
 9517           x->data[i] = x4[perm[3] - 1];
 9518           ib = 0;
 9519         }
 9520       }
 9521     }
 9522   
 9523     wOffset = (b_n - nNaNs) - 1;
 9524     if (ib > 0) {
 9525       for (i = 0; i < 4; i++) {
 9526         perm[i] = 0;
 9527       }
 9528   
 9529       if (ib == 1) {
 9530         perm[0] = 1;
 9531       } else if (ib == 2) {
 9532         if (x4[0] >= x4[1]) {
 9533           perm[0] = 1;
 9534           perm[1] = 2;
 9535         } else {
 9536           perm[0] = 2;
 9537           perm[1] = 1;
 9538         }
 9539       } else if (x4[0] >= x4[1]) {
 9540         if (x4[1] >= x4[2]) {
 9541           perm[0] = 1;
 9542           perm[1] = 2;
 9543           perm[2] = 3;
 9544         } else if (x4[0] >= x4[2]) {
 9545           perm[0] = 1;
 9546           perm[1] = 3;
 9547           perm[2] = 2;
 9548         } else {
 9549           perm[0] = 3;
 9550           perm[1] = 1;
 9551           perm[2] = 2;
 9552         }
 9553       } else if (x4[0] >= x4[2]) {
 9554         perm[0] = 2;
 9555         perm[1] = 1;
 9556         perm[2] = 3;
 9557       } else if (x4[1] >= x4[2]) {
 9558         perm[0] = 2;
 9559         perm[1] = 3;
 9560         perm[2] = 1;
 9561       } else {
 9562         perm[0] = 3;
 9563         perm[1] = 2;
 9564         perm[2] = 1;
 9565       }
 9566   
 9567       for (k = 1; k <= ib; k++) {
 9568         idx->data[(wOffset - ib) + k] = idx4[perm[k - 1] - 1];
 9569         x->data[(wOffset - ib) + k] = x4[perm[k - 1] - 1];
 9570       }
 9571     }
 9572   
 9573     i = (nNaNs >> 1) + 1;
 9574     for (k = 1; k < i; k++) {
 9575       ib = idx->data[wOffset + k];
 9576       idx->data[wOffset + k] = idx->data[b_n - k];
 9577       idx->data[b_n - k] = ib;
 9578       x->data[wOffset + k] = xwork->data[b_n - k];
 9579       x->data[b_n - k] = xwork->data[wOffset + k];
 9580     }
 9581   
 9582     if ((nNaNs & 1) != 0) {
 9583       x->data[wOffset + i] = xwork->data[wOffset + i];
 9584     }
 9585   
 9586     nNonNaN = n - nNaNs;
 9587     ib = 2;
 9588     if (nNonNaN > 1) {
 9589       if (n >= 256) {
 9590         nBlocks = nNonNaN >> 8;
 9591         if (nBlocks > 0) {
 9592           for (i3 = 1; i3 <= nBlocks; i3++) {
 9593             i4 = ((i3 - 1) << 8) - 1;
 9594             for (b_n = 0; b_n < 6; b_n++) {
 9595               n = 1 << (b_n + 2);
 9596               bLen2 = n << 1;
 9597               nPairs = 256 >> (b_n + 3);
 9598               for (k = 1; k <= nPairs; k++) {
 9599                 ib = i4 + (k - 1) * bLen2;
 9600                 for (i = 1; i <= bLen2; i++) {
 9601                   b_iwork[i - 1] = idx->data[ib + i];
 9602                   b_xwork[i - 1] = x->data[ib + i];
 9603                 }
 9604   
 9605                 wOffset = 0;
 9606                 i = n;
 9607                 do {
 9608                   exitg1 = 0;
 9609                   ib++;
 9610                   if (b_xwork[wOffset] >= b_xwork[i]) {
 9611                     idx->data[ib] = b_iwork[wOffset];
 9612                     x->data[ib] = b_xwork[wOffset];
 9613                     if (wOffset + 1 < n) {
 9614                       wOffset++;
 9615                     } else {
 9616                       exitg1 = 1;
 9617                     }
 9618                   } else {
 9619                     idx->data[ib] = b_iwork[i];
 9620                     x->data[ib] = b_xwork[i];
 9621                     if (i + 1 < bLen2) {
 9622                       i++;
 9623                     } else {
 9624                       i = ib - wOffset;
 9625                       while (wOffset + 1 <= n) {
 9626                         idx->data[(i + wOffset) + 1] = b_iwork[wOffset];
 9627                         x->data[(i + wOffset) + 1] = b_xwork[wOffset];
 9628                         wOffset++;
 9629                       }
 9630   
 9631                       exitg1 = 1;
 9632                     }
 9633                   }
 9634                 } while (exitg1 == 0);
 9635               }
 9636             }
 9637           }
 9638   
 9639           ib = nBlocks << 8;
 9640           i = nNonNaN - ib;
 9641           if (i > 0) {
 9642             merge_block(idx, x, ib, i, 2, iwork, xwork);
 9643           }
 9644   
 9645           ib = 8;
 9646         }
 9647       }
 9648   
 9649       merge_block(idx, x, 0, nNonNaN, ib, iwork, xwork);
 9650     }
 9651   
 9652     if ((nNaNs > 0) && (nNonNaN > 0)) {
 9653       for (k = 0; k + 1 <= nNaNs; k++) {
 9654         xwork->data[k] = x->data[nNonNaN + k];
 9655         iwork->data[k] = idx->data[nNonNaN + k];
 9656       }
 9657   
 9658       for (k = nNonNaN - 1; k + 1 > 0; k--) {
 9659         x->data[nNaNs + k] = x->data[k];
 9660         idx->data[nNaNs + k] = idx->data[k];
 9661       }
 9662   
 9663       for (k = 0; k + 1 <= nNaNs; k++) {
 9664         x->data[k] = xwork->data[k];
 9665         idx->data[k] = iwork->data[k];
 9666       }
 9667     }
 9668   
 9669     emxFree_real32_T(&xwork);
 9670     emxFree_int32_T(&iwork);
 9671   }
 9672   
 9673   static void squeeze(const emxArray_real_T *a, emxArray_real_T *b)
 9674   {
 9675     int k;
 9676     int i11;
 9677     int sqsz[3];
 9678     k = 3;
 9679     while ((k > 2) && (a->size[2] == 1)) {
 9680       k = 2;
 9681     }
 9682   
 9683     if (k <= 2) {
 9684       sqsz[1] = a->size[1];
 9685       i11 = b->size[0] * b->size[1];
 9686       b->size[0] = 1;
 9687       b->size[1] = sqsz[1];
 9688       emxEnsureCapacity_real_T(b, i11);
 9689       i11 = a->size[1] * a->size[2];
 9690       for (k = 0; k + 1 <= i11; k++) {
 9691         b->data[k] = a->data[k];
 9692       }
 9693     } else {
 9694       for (i11 = 0; i11 < 3; i11++) {
 9695         sqsz[i11] = 1;
 9696       }
 9697   
 9698       k = 0;
 9699       if (a->size[1] != 1) {
 9700         sqsz[0] = a->size[1];
 9701         k = 1;
 9702       }
 9703   
 9704       if (a->size[2] != 1) {
 9705         sqsz[k] = a->size[2];
 9706       }
 9707   
 9708       i11 = b->size[0] * b->size[1];
 9709       b->size[0] = sqsz[0];
 9710       b->size[1] = sqsz[1];
 9711       emxEnsureCapacity_real_T(b, i11);
 9712       i11 = a->size[1] * a->size[2];
 9713       for (k = 0; k + 1 <= i11; k++) {
 9714         b->data[k] = a->data[k];
 9715       }
 9716     }
 9717   }

 9719   static void subPixelLocation(const emxArray_real32_T *metric, emxArray_real_T
 9720     *loc)
 9721   {
 9722     int i48;
 9723     int id;
 9724     emxArray_real32_T *b_metric;
 9725     int loop_ub;
 9726     int i49;
 9727     int b_loop_ub;
 9728     double loc_data[2];
 9729     int loc_size[1];
 9730     emxArray_boolean_T b_loc_data;
 9731     boolean_T c_loc_data[2];
 9732     int i50;
 9733     float subPixelLoc_data[2];
 9734     int i51;
 9735     int i52;
 9736     int i53;
 9737     int c_loop_ub;
 9738     float x;
 9739     float beta[6];
 9740     float y;
 9741     float b_x[2];
 9742     float d_loc_data[2];
 9743     i48 = loc->size[0];
 9744     id = 0;
 9745     emxInit_real32_T(&b_metric, 2);
 9746     while (id <= i48 - 1) {
 9747       loop_ub = loc->size[1];
 9748       for (i49 = 0; i49 < loop_ub; i49++) {
 9749         loc_data[i49] = loc->data[id + loc->size[0] * i49];
 9750       }
 9751   
 9752       b_loop_ub = loc->size[1];
 9753       loc_size[0] = b_loop_ub;
 9754       for (i49 = 0; i49 < b_loop_ub; i49++) {
 9755         c_loc_data[i49] = (loc_data[i49] < 3.0);
 9756       }
 9757   
 9758       b_loc_data.data = (boolean_T *)&c_loc_data;
 9759       b_loc_data.size = (int *)&loc_size;
 9760       b_loc_data.allocatedSize = 2;
 9761       b_loc_data.numDimensions = 1;
 9762       b_loc_data.canFreeData = false;
 9763       if (any(&b_loc_data) || (loc->data[id] > ((double)metric->size[1] - 2.0) -
 9764            1.0) || (loc->data[id + loc->size[0]] > ((double)metric->size[0] - 2.0)
 9765                     - 1.0)) {
 9766         for (i49 = 0; i49 < loop_ub; i49++) {
 9767           subPixelLoc_data[i49] = (float)loc_data[i49];
 9768         }
 9769       } else {
 9770         if (loc->data[id + loc->size[0]] - 2.0 > loc->data[id + loc->size[0]] +
 9771             2.0) {
 9772           i49 = 0;
 9773           i50 = 0;
 9774         } else {
 9775           i49 = (int)(loc->data[id + loc->size[0]] - 2.0) - 1;
 9776           i50 = (int)(loc->data[id + loc->size[0]] + 2.0);
 9777         }
 9778   
 9779         if (loc->data[id] - 2.0 > loc->data[id] + 2.0) {
 9780           i51 = 0;
 9781           i52 = 0;
 9782         } else {
 9783           i51 = (int)(loc->data[id] - 2.0) - 1;
 9784           i52 = (int)(loc->data[id] + 2.0);
 9785         }
 9786   
 9787         i53 = b_metric->size[0] * b_metric->size[1];
 9788         b_metric->size[0] = i50 - i49;
 9789         b_metric->size[1] = i52 - i51;
 9790         emxEnsureCapacity_real32_T(b_metric, i53);
 9791         b_loop_ub = i52 - i51;
 9792         for (i52 = 0; i52 < b_loop_ub; i52++) {
 9793           c_loop_ub = i50 - i49;
 9794           for (i53 = 0; i53 < c_loop_ub; i53++) {
 9795             b_metric->data[i53 + b_metric->size[0] * i52] = metric->data[(i49 +
 9796               i53) + metric->size[0] * (i51 + i52)];
 9797           }
 9798         }
 9799   
 9800         for (i49 = 0; i49 < 6; i49++) {
 9801           beta[i49] = 0.0F;
 9802           for (i50 = 0; i50 < 25; i50++) {
 9803             x = beta[i49] + (float)X[i49 + 6 * i50] * b_metric->data[i50];
 9804             beta[i49] = x;
 9805           }
 9806         }
 9807   
 9808         x = -(2.0F * beta[1] * beta[2] - beta[3] * beta[4]) / (4.0F * beta[0] *
 9809           beta[1] - beta[4] * beta[4]);
 9810         y = -(2.0F * beta[0] * beta[3] - beta[2] * beta[4]) / (4.0F * beta[0] *
 9811           beta[1] - beta[4] * beta[4]);
 9812         if ((!((!rtIsInfF(x)) && (!rtIsNaNF(x)))) || (std::abs(x) > 2.0F) ||
 9813             (!((!rtIsInfF(y)) && (!rtIsNaNF(y)))) || (std::abs(y) > 2.0F)) {
 9814           x = 0.0F;
 9815           y = 0.0F;
 9816         }
 9817   
 9818         for (i49 = 0; i49 < loop_ub; i49++) {
 9819           d_loc_data[i49] = (float)loc_data[i49];
 9820         }
 9821   
 9822         b_x[0] = x;
 9823         b_x[1] = y;
 9824         loop_ub = 2;
 9825         for (i49 = 0; i49 < 2; i49++) {
 9826           subPixelLoc_data[i49] = d_loc_data[i49] + b_x[i49];
 9827         }
 9828       }
 9829   
 9830       for (i49 = 0; i49 < loop_ub; i49++) {
 9831         loc->data[id + loc->size[0] * i49] = subPixelLoc_data[i49];
 9832       }
 9833   
 9834       id++;
 9835     }
 9836   
 9837     emxFree_real32_T(&b_metric);
 9838   }
 9839   
 9840   static void subPixelLocationImpl_init()
 9841   {
 9842     static const double dv1[150] = { 0.028571428571428574, 0.028571428571428574,

 9879   static void toPoints(const c_vision_internal_calibration_c *b_this,
 9880                        emxArray_real_T *points, double boardSize[2])
 9881   {
 9882     emxArray_boolean_T *c_this;
 9883     int i32;
 9884     int loop_ub;
 9885     double numPoints;
 9886     emxArray_real_T *x;
 9887     int b_loop_ub;
 9888     int i33;
 9889     emxInit_boolean_T1(&c_this, 1);
 9890     i32 = c_this->size[0];
 9891     c_this->size[0] = b_this->BoardIdx->size[0] * b_this->BoardIdx->size[1];
 9892     emxEnsureCapacity_boolean_T1(c_this, i32);
 9893     loop_ub = b_this->BoardIdx->size[0] * b_this->BoardIdx->size[1];
 9894     for (i32 = 0; i32 < loop_ub; i32++) {
 9895       c_this->data[i32] = (b_this->BoardIdx->data[i32] == 0.0);
 9896     }
 9897   
 9898     if (any(c_this)) {
 9899       i32 = points->size[0] * points->size[1];
 9900       points->size[0] = 0;
 9901       points->size[1] = 0;
 9902       emxEnsureCapacity_real_T(points, i32);
 9903       for (i32 = 0; i32 < 2; i32++) {
 9904         boardSize[i32] = 0.0;
 9905       }
 9906     } else {
 9907       numPoints = (double)b_this->BoardCoords->size[0] * (double)
 9908         b_this->BoardCoords->size[1];
 9909       i32 = points->size[0] * points->size[1];
 9910       points->size[0] = (int)numPoints;
 9911       points->size[1] = 2;
 9912       emxEnsureCapacity_real_T(points, i32);
 9913       loop_ub = (int)numPoints << 1;
 9914       for (i32 = 0; i32 < loop_ub; i32++) {
 9915         points->data[i32] = 0.0;
 9916       }
 9917   
 9918       emxInit_real_T1(&x, 2);
 9919       loop_ub = b_this->BoardCoords->size[0];
 9920       b_loop_ub = b_this->BoardCoords->size[1];
 9921       i32 = x->size[0] * x->size[1];
 9922       x->size[0] = b_loop_ub;
 9923       x->size[1] = loop_ub;
 9924       emxEnsureCapacity_real_T(x, i32);
 9925       for (i32 = 0; i32 < loop_ub; i32++) {
 9926         for (i33 = 0; i33 < b_loop_ub; i33++) {
 9927           x->data[i33 + x->size[0] * i32] = b_this->BoardCoords->data[i32 +
 9928             b_this->BoardCoords->size[0] * i33];
 9929         }
 9930       }
 9931   
 9932       loop_ub = x->size[0] * x->size[1];
 9933       for (i32 = 0; i32 < loop_ub; i32++) {
 9934         points->data[i32] = x->data[i32];
 9935       }
 9936   
 9937       loop_ub = b_this->BoardCoords->size[0];
 9938       b_loop_ub = b_this->BoardCoords->size[1];
 9939       i32 = x->size[0] * x->size[1];
 9940       x->size[0] = b_loop_ub;
 9941       x->size[1] = loop_ub;
 9942       emxEnsureCapacity_real_T(x, i32);
 9943       for (i32 = 0; i32 < loop_ub; i32++) {
 9944         for (i33 = 0; i33 < b_loop_ub; i33++) {
 9945           x->data[i33 + x->size[0] * i32] = b_this->BoardCoords->data[(i32 +
 9946             b_this->BoardCoords->size[0] * i33) + b_this->BoardCoords->size[0] *
 9947             b_this->BoardCoords->size[1]];
 9948         }
 9949       }
 9950   
 9951       loop_ub = x->size[0] * x->size[1];
 9952       for (i32 = 0; i32 < loop_ub; i32++) {
 9953         points->data[i32 + points->size[0]] = x->data[i32];
 9954       }
 9955   
 9956       emxFree_real_T(&x);
 9957       boardSize[0] = (double)b_this->BoardCoords->size[1] + 1.0;
 9958       boardSize[1] = (double)b_this->BoardCoords->size[0] + 1.0;
 9959     }
 9960   
 9961     emxFree_boolean_T(&c_this);
 9962   }

 9965            boardSize[2])
 9966   {

 9968     c_vision_internal_calibration_c lobj_5;

10020     emxEnsureCapacity_real32_T(b_Ix, Ix);
10021     Ix = b_Ix->size[0];
10022     loop_ub = b_Ix->size[1];
10023     loop_ub *= Ix;
10024     for (Ix = 0; Ix < loop_ub; Ix++) {
10025       b_Ix->data[Ix] *= Iy->data[Ix];
10026     }

10030     emxInit_int32_T(&r0, 1);

10032     find_peaks(cxy, points0);
10033     psiz = cxy->size[0];
10034     loop_ub = points0->size[0];
10035     Ix = r0->size[0];
10036     r0->size[0] = loop_ub;
10037     emxEnsureCapacity_int32_T(r0, Ix);

10040         points0->data[Ix] - 1);
10041     }
10042

10050     }

10053     board0 = growCheckerboard(points0, b_cxy, Ix2, Iy2, b_Ix, 0.0, &lobj_0,
10054       &lobj_1, &lobj_2);

10057     loop_ub = points0->size[0];

10077       &lobj_3, &lobj_4, &lobj_5);
